(1, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicysteakandmontere_88037\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spicysteakandmontere_88037_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beef enchiladas \n', ' Mexican beef enchiladas – tortillas packed with beef mince and beans and smothered with cheese – are easy to make and a great crowd-pleaser. \n', 30, 90, 4, 18),
(2, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/choc_chip_pan_cookie_45509\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/choc_chip_pan_cookie_45509_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate chip pan cookie\n', ' Here’s a quick way to get the homemade cookie flavour but without the faff of divvying up the dough. It’s all made in one pan and cooked slowly on the hob till you have a lovely crust, but a gooey centre.\n', 30, 30, 4, 9),
(3, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_tikka_masala_11482\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_tikka_masala_11482_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tom\'s chicken tikka masala\n', ' Tom Kerridge\'s healthier version of chicken tikka masala is a real crowd-pleaser. Leave for at least 4 hours for the chicken to marinate.\n Each serving provides 640 kcal, 52g protein, 88g carbohydrates (of which 20g sugars), 6.5g fat (of which 1g saturates), 10g fibre and 0.9g salt.\n', 480, 120, 4, 25),
(4, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/navajo_lamb_stew_63964\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/navajo_lamb_stew_63964_16x9.jpg\n', 'Navajo lamb stew\n', ' This slow-cooked lamb stew makes a hearty dinner and the dumplings provide extra comfort factor. \n', 30, 120, 4, 27),
(5, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mutton_chops_with_potato_75289\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mutton_chops_with_potato_75289_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mutton chops with potato and turnip gratin \n', ' Mutton, potatoes and turnips are given a bit of flair with sauce gribiche and lashings of cream.\n', 30, 90, 6, 27),
(6, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_slow-cooked_48143\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spiced_slow-cooked_48143_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spiced slow-cooked mutton with Mexican chillies\n', ' A leg of lamb is given a Mexican kick with potent spices and chillies. It needs to be prepared a few hours in advance but there\'s no tricky techniques involved. \n This meal, if served as six portions, provides 646kcal, 64g protein, 19g carbohydrate (of which 12g sugars), 29g fat (of which 11g saturates), 5g fibre and 0.8g salt.\n', 480, 120, 6, 18),
(7, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smokey_mutton_sloppy_joe_19958\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smokey_mutton_sloppy_joe_19958_16x9.jpg\n', 'Smoky mutton Sloppy Joe with crispy lamb’s breast\n', ' Impress your friends with these tasty lamb Sloppy Joe’s, perfect for a party. If you don\'t have time to make the crispy lamb\'s breast garnish you can substitute with crisps. \n', 480, 120, 4, 23),
(8, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegetable_risotto_18315\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegetable_risotto_18315_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegetable risotto \n', ' A very easy risotto, needing no unusual ingredients and made extra delicious with the addition of grated lemon zest. To keep it simple, rather than adding the stock gradually, pour it all in at the beginning, then stir regularly as the rice simmers.\n', 30, 30, 4, 17),
(9, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spaghetti_and_meatballs_69603\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spaghetti_and_meatballs_69603_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spaghetti and meatballs\n', ' A simple tomato sauce with lots of flavour is perfect for spaghetti and meatballs. A weeknight classic. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n', 30, 90, 4, 11),
(10, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pauls_mums_jam_tarts_68845\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pauls_mums_jam_tarts_68845_16x9.jpg\n', 'Paul’s mum’s jam tarts\n', ' This ‘incredibly difficult’ recipe was sent in by my mum. You can use any jam in the tarts, whichever suits your taste buds best. Top tip from my mum: it’s a good way to use up leftover pastry. I hope I do you proud mum!\n', 30, 30, 20, 4),
(11, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemonverbenacremebru_91367\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02828qx.jpg\n', 'Lemon verbena crème brûlée with poached pear and spelt shortbread\n', ' None\n', 90, 120, 4, 14),
(12, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/buffalo_kebabs_with_54909\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/buffalo_kebabs_with_54909_16x9.jpg\n', 'Buffalo kebabs with cauliflower coleslaw\n', ' Traditionally these kebabs are made with buffalo, but beef sirloin also works well. They are best cooked on a barbecue, but if the weather fails you try cooking them under a hot grill instead. \n For this recipe you need wooden skewers pre-soaked in water.\n', 90, 30, 4, 20),
(13, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicy_mussels_with_50599\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spicy_mussels_with_50599_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spicy mussels with chorizo and cider\n', ' These salty mussels and rich, spicy sauce get a fresh boost from the parsley. Serve with sourdough for a hearty meal.\n', 30, 30, 2, 13),
(14, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sweet_potato_rsti_98950\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sweet_potato_rsti_98950_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sweet potato rösti\n', ' Inexpensive and quick to prepare, these delicious sweet potato röstis work brilliantly with a salad, as a burger filling or as a lunch box snack. To make this vegan, swap the mayonnaise for vegan mayonnaise.\n', 30, 30, 8, 13),
(15, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tagliatelle_with_23536\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tagliatelle_with_23536_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tagliatelle with mushrooms and pancetta\n', ' A simple pasta dish made with porcini and wild mushrooms for an extra special touch. Stir in a little cream at the end if you are feeling indulgent.\n', 30, 10, 2, 11),
(16, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/marys_lemon_meringue_pie_02330\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/marys_lemon_meringue_pie_02330_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lemon meringue pie\n', ' Mary Berry shows you how to make an easy lemon meringue pie with no soggy bottoms in sight.\n', 30, 90, 8, 10),
(17, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/clottedcreamricepudd_89100\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02827vt.jpg\n', 'Clotted cream rice pudding with raspberries and orange caramel\n', ' Take rice pudding to the most indulgent level with clotted cream and orange caramel.\n', 30, 90, 1, 9),
(18, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/clams_and_scallops_in_a_62146\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/honey_and_soy-glazed_26258\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/honey_and_soy-glazed_26258_16x9.jpg\n', ' Honey and soy glazed trout\n Trout makes a good substitute for salmon in this Asian-inspired quick fish dish from the Hairy Bikers. Serve with garlic bok choi.\n', 90, 30, 4, 14),
(19, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/orange_blossom_baklava_11703\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/orange_blossom_baklava_11703_16x9.jpg\n', 'Orange blossom baklava \n', ' This is my favourite combination of chocolate and orange, and I like to eat it the way we did in Turkey – with lashings of clotted cream on top. They can also be decorated with edible golden stars. \n', 30, 90, 16, 14),
(20, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/devilishredcabbage_8076\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/devilishredcabbage_8076_16x9.jpg\n', 'Christmas red cabbage\n', ' Try this mouthwatering winter warmer of braised red cabbage stewed with apples and spices. Perfect with a roast dinner.\n', 30, 30, 4, 10),
(21, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickpea_spinach_and_egg_50755\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chickpea_spinach_and_egg_50755_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chickpea, spinach and egg curry\n', ' This vegetarian low-calorie chickpea curry makes a wonderful, easy after-work meal, and is ready in less than 20 minutes. It\'s also vegan if you leave out the egg. \n Each serving provides 441 kcal, 26g protein, 92g carbohydrates (of which 8.5g sugars), 20g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 15g fibre and 0.6g salt. \n \n With a GI of 45 this meal is high protein, low GI.\n', 30, 30, 2, 16),
(22, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/open_salmon_and_pesto_56820\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/open_salmon_and_pesto_56820_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pesto and salmon parcels\n', ' This fuss-free and thrifty tart is a doddle to prepare and uses ingredients from the freezer. Defrost the fish and pastry overnight for a speedy after-work supper.\n Each serving provides 752kcal, 33g protein, 55g carbohydrate (of which 3g sugars), 43g fat (of which 14g saturates), 3.5g fibre and 1g salt.\n \n', 120, 30, 4, 10),
(23, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/nachos_92445\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/nachos_92445_16x9.jpg\n', 'Nachos\n', ' If you haven\'t learned how to make your own nachos, this is your moment.  Ellis Barrie shows you how easy it is to make the perfect snack for hungry mates.\n', 30, 30, 2, 17),
(24, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salmon_asparagus_and_11981\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quick_naan_bread_13358\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02bmprr.jpg\n', ' Quick naan bread\n This quick and easy naan bread uses baking powder for fluffiness and requires very little kneading, making it ready in half an hour.\n', 30, 30, 8, 9),
(25, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/french_apple_tart_with_70368\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/french_apple_tart_with_70368_16x9.jpg\n', 'French apple tart\n', ' This easy apple tart uses shop bought puff pastry to speed things up. Laced with calvados and topped with soft Chantilly – look out for all-butter puff for the best flavour.\n', 30, 90, 8, 11),
(26, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mince_pies_16839\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mince_pies_16839_16x9.jpg\n', 'Homemade mince pies\n', ' Mince pies with homemade mincemeat and pastry.  Add a grating of orange zest to your pastry for a unique flavour. \n', 480, 90, 12, 19),
(27, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salmon_wellington_86468\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/salmon_wellington_86468_16x9.jpg\n', 'Salmon en croûte \n', ' A whole salmon en croûte is a lovely Christmas party centrepiece. This simple recipe uses readymade pastry to make it quick and easy.\n', 30, 90, 12, 12),
(28, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/puy_lentil_bolognaise_40407\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/puy_lentil_bolognaise_40407_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegetarian bolognese\n', ' This delicious recipe for vegetarian bolognese sauce from Eat Well for Less makes enough for 2 meals. Brilliant with spaghetti or in a lasagne. \n Each serving provides 296 kcal, 13g protein, 48g carbohydrates (of which 10g sugars), 4g fat (of which 2g saturates), 8.5g fibre and 0.3g salt.\n', 30, 90, 8, 17),
(29, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/one-pan_chicken_68593\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/one-pan_chicken_68593_16x9.jpg\n', 'One-pan roast chicken dinner\n', ' Vegetables, potatoes, chicken, peas and bacon all roasted in one pan. A simple and tasty all-in-one-roast chicken recipe with minimal washing up.\n', 30, 120, 4, 16),
(30, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/barmbrack_parfait_with_87190\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_satay_noodles_95490\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_satay_noodles_95490_16x9.jpg\n', ' Chicken satay noodles\n Peanut butter and coconut milk make a quick DIY satay sauce. Pack out this filling noodle dish with plenty of fresh veg and strips of chicken or turkey.\n Each serving provides 747 kcal, 46g protein, 84g carbohydrates (of which 14g sugars), 23g fat (of which 9g saturates), 10g fibre and 2.7g salt.\n', 30, 30, 4, 19),
(31, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushroom_and_parsnip_91300\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mushroom_and_parsnip_91300_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mushroom and parsnip rösti pie\n', ' A hearty, warming vegetarian mushroom pie that would satisfy the richest and most lavish tastebuds, but light enough that it won’t send you to sleep. \n', 30, 120, 6, 18),
(32, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ratatouille_lasagne_28209\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/ratatouille_lasagne_28209_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lighter vegetable lasagne\n', ' A vegetarian family lasagne that’s ready in just 45 minutes. Cottage cheese makes it a healthier option, plus you don’t need to make the traditional cheese sauce. Serve with a green salad or sweetcorn for even more of your five-a-day. Each serving provides 285 kcal, 20g protein, 33g carbohydrates (of which 11g sugars), 7g fat (of which 3g saturates), 6g fibre and 0.8g salt.\n \n For this recipe you\'ll need a 20x28cm/8x11in ovenproof dish.\n \n \n', 30, 90, 4, 16),
(33, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chorizo_scotch_eggs_with_45548\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p017tm3j.jpg\n', 'Chorizo scotch eggs with paprika potato salad\n', ' Scotch eggs are a real treat and making your own is surprisingly simple. Chorizo gives it a tasty twist. \n', 30, 90, 4, 16),
(34, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salted_caramel_and_apple_43744\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/salted_caramel_and_apple_43744_16x9.jpg\n', 'Salted caramel and apple rolls\n', ' Part Danish pastry, part sticky bun, these upmarket salted caramel tea-time rolls are simply delicious\n', 30, 120, 12, 11),
(35, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/steakandkidneypie_73308\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/steakandkidneypie_73308_16x9.jpg\n', 'Steak and kidney pie\n', ' Make the most of inexpensive cuts of beef for this steak and kidney pie recipe - meltingly tender after long slow cooking.\n', 30, 120, 4, 12),
(36, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spongecake_1284\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spongecake_1284_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sponge cake\n', ' A step-by-step recipe for a foolproof, easy sponge cake with only 5 ingredients. A classic sponge cake can be jazzed up with whipped cream and seasonal fruit, or with your favourite jam or fruit curd.\n', 30, 30, 8, 6),
(37, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushroom_ale_pie_90722\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mushroom_ale_pie_90722_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mushroom and ale pie\n', ' A delightful wintry vegan pie with rich mushrooms and sweet shallots that will make your cold nights a lot warmer. Vegan comfort food at its best. \n Each serving provides 552 kcal, 10g protein, 67g carbohydrate (of which 13g sugars), 22g fat (of which 3g saturates), 6g fibre and 1.3g salt.\n', 30, 120, 6, 22),
(38, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cheesy_bean_and_lentil_71817\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cheesy_bean_and_lentil_71817_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cheesy bean and lentil bake \n', ' This hearty veggie bake can be prepared in advance and topped with cheese and breadcrumbs just before cooking.\n Based on six servings, each portion provides 361 kcal, 17g protein, 36g carbohydrate (of which 10g sugars), 15g fat (of which 6g saturates), 7g fibre and 0.7g salt.\n', 30, 90, 4, 19),
(39, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vanillaandgingerbrea_84059\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02827vt.jpg\n', 'Vanilla and gingerbread cheesecake\n', ' Use ready-made ginger cake as a base in these invidual cheesecakes topped with stawberries infused in balsamic vinegar.\n', 480, 10, 8, 7),
(40, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sprouts_with_chestnuts_87565\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sprouts_with_chestnuts_87565_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sprouts with chestnuts and pancetta\n', ' Mary Berry\'s sprouts with bacon or panchetta and chestnuts make a lovely alternative to the boiled or steamed varieties at Christmas. \n', 30, 30, 6, 8),
(41, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pakistani_chicken_pulao_13179\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pakistani_chicken_pulao_13179_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pakistani chicken pulao\n', ' The chicken in this classic Pakistani pulao recipe cooks in a spicy stock which is then used to flavour the rice. \n', 120, 90, 6, 22),
(42, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_pigeon_breasts_73654\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/coffee_chocolate_and_px_77531\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tortapasquale_88435\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tortapasquale_88435_16x9.jpg\n Easter spinach pie (torta pasquale)\n A beautiful vegetarian Easter feast, this authentic Italian pie is stuffed with fresh greens and rich eggs and is perfect for eating throughout the summer.\n', 30, 90, 6, 23),
(43, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tapioca_porridge_with_13213\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tapioca_porridge_with_13213_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tapioca porridge with baked rhubarb \n', ' Tapioca pudding is transformed into a lovely comforting Suhoor breakfast with rose-flavoured rhubarb and pistachios.  This eats well warm or cold.\n', 30, 90, 1, 10),
(44, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/scones_1285\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/scones_1285_16x9.jpg\n', 'Scones\n', ' Scones are the easiest British teatime treat.  Feel free to customise yours with dried fruit or a pinch of spice to make this basic scones recipe your own.\n Each serving provides 150 kcal, 3.5g protein, 20g carbohydrates (of which 3.5g sugars), 6g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 1g fibre and 0.4g salt.\n', 30, 30, 10, 6),
(45, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/baked_aloo_gobi_with_32681\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/baked_aloo_gobi_with_32681_16x9.jpg\n', 'Baked aloo gobi with flatbreads\n', ' This vegetarian whole-baked cauliflower and potato curry can also be made suitable for vegans. \n', 30, 120, 4, 19),
(46, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_shepherds_pie_68249\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spiced_shepherds_pie_68249_16x9.jpg\n', 'Quick shepherd’s pie\n', ' This cheap, quick shepherd’s pie uses ingredients straight from the freezer - no need for boiling and mashing potatoes!\n', 30, 90, 6, 15),
