(156, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mini_sausage_plaits_04508\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mini_sausage_plaits_04508_16x9.jpg\n', 'Black pudding sausage rolls\n', ' Turn up to a picnic or party with these and you are sure to impress your friends and family. \n', 120, 30, 12, 14),
