(171, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lamb_breast_with_08232\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p017tm3j.jpg\n', 'Slow-cooked lamb breast with vegetables and an egg vinaigrette\n', ' Slow-cooking lamb breast turns this cheap cut of meat into something special. \n Equipment and preparation: For this recipe you need a food processor. \n', 30, 120, 4, 17),
