(355, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chilli_beef_rendang_47873\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chilli_beef_rendang_47873_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chilli beef rendang\n', ' The list of ingredients may be long, but this much-loved South-East Asian curry is simple to prepare.\n', 120, 120, 4, 23),
(356, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/grilled_chicken_shatkora_00658\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/grilled_chicken_shatkora_00658_16x9.jpg\n', 'Grilled chicken shatkora with pickle and chapatis\n', ' Shatkora is a citrus fruit that is commonly cooked with in Bangladesh. You can find it in large Asian grocers. (If you can\'t find them, try lemons instead.)\n', 30, 0, 8, 16),
(357, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/seabass_ceviche_on_corn_19536\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_and_hazelnut_81026\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fool-proof_green_salad_90764\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fool-proof_green_salad_90764_16x9.jpg\n Foolproof green salad \n There is nothing worse than a boring bowl of green leaves served at a table with a meal. I like to add some crunchy vegetables to it and I have a trick to let you make this ahead so the lettuce doesn’t wilt even though you prepared it a couple of hours ago!\n', 30, 0, 10, 16),
(358, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/aubergine_and_bean_82086\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/aubergine_and_bean_82086_16x9.jpg\n', 'Aubergine and bean casserole\n', ' Balance healthy ingredients beautifully with this vegan casserole recipe.\n This meal served as six portions provides 217 kcal, 8g protein, 40g carbohydrate (of which 28g sugars), 3g fat (of which 0.5g saturates), 9g fibre and 1.9g salt per portion. \n', 30, 90, 4, 16),
(359, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tuna_tostadas_20585\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mediterraneanstylela_83720\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mediterraneanstylela_83720_16x9.jpg\n', ' Mediterranean-style lamb chops\n A perfect weeknight supper - simple, flavourful chop served with lots of healthy Mediterranean vegetables and a little feta.\n This meal is low calorie  and provides 200 kcal, 9g protein, 15g carbohydrate (of which 14g sugars), 11.5g fat (of which 4g saturates), 7g fibre and 0.8g salt per portion.\n', 30, 90, 4, 12),
(360, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beefasparagusandmang_85921\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Beef, asparagus and mangetout stir fry\n', ' Full of flavour and so simple. Substitute green pepper for the asparagus if it\'s not in season.\n', 30, 10, 2, 14),
(361, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/dark_and_sumptuous_53597\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/dark_and_sumptuous_53597_16x9.jpg\n', 'Dark and sumptuous chocolate cake\n', ' A vegan chocolate cake to die for from Nigella Lawson\'s Simply Nigella.\n For this recipe you will need a leakproof 20cm/8in springform cake tin.\n', 30, 90, 10, 15),
(362, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_burger_with_98749\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beef_burger_with_98749_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beef burgers with beetroot and carrot slaw\n', ' You must make Mary Berry\'s burger recipe. The crunchy, fiery slaw is perfect alongside or served separately as a salad.\n', 30, 10, 6, 25),
(363, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/parsnip_sweet_potato_and_66305\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/parsnip_sweet_potato_and_66305_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cheesy parsnip and sweet potato tarts\n', ' The festive flavours of sage and parsnip make these tarts a great choice for vegetarians on Christmas day. \n', 90, 120, 6, 15),
(364, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_shepherds_pie_05111\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_shepherds_pie_05111_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan shepherd’s pie \n', ' This delicious, savoury vegan shepherd\'s pie freezes very well, so make in individual portions if you prefer, or freeze the leftovers. The secret ingredient is nutritional yeast, a great vegan ingredient that lends a cheesy flavour to the mash topping. Serve with lots of freshly cooked green vegetables.\n Each serving provides 441 kcal, 18g protein, 54g carbohydrate (of which 10g sugars), 13g fat (of which 2g saturates), 12g fibre and 1g salt.\n \n', 90, 120, 6, 25),
(365, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lobsterthermidor_73972\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lobsterthermidor_73972_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lobster thermidor\n', ' Such a treat on Christmas Eve or for any deluxe special occasion. The chips are gilding the lily, but why not?\n', 30, 90, 2, 14),
(366, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ackee_and_saltfish_with_73421\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027v8xm.jpg\n', 'Ackee and saltfish with potato and plantain röstis\n', ' Ackee and saltfish is a spicy Caribbean classic and is combined here with fried plantain röstis for a quick but flavourful meal. \n', 30, 90, 4, 22),
(367, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushroom_stroganoff_with_83256\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mushroom_stroganoff_with_83256_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy mushroom stroganoff\n', ' A vegetarian mushroom stroganoff that\'s as rich and delicious as its meaty cousin. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n', 30, 30, 4, 12),
(368, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ragoutoffreshwatercr_88577\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07f404k.jpg\n', 'Ragoût of crayfish, girolles, fregola pasta, courgettes and watercress cream\n', ' None\n', 90, 90, 4, 17),
(369, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vietnamese_beef_and_57283\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vietnamese_beef_and_57283_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vietnamese beef and lettuce wraps\n', ' Try serving strips of steak on lettuce with a sharp, sweet blend of Vietnamese flavours. Use a lean cut of beef such as rump or flank steak that\'s packed full of flavour and low in fat.\n', 120, 30, 4, 21);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(370, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/warm_chicken_salad_03629\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/warm_chicken_salad_03629_16x9.jpg\n', 'Warm chicken salad\n', ' A gorgeous chicken salad that can be served warm or cold, perfect for a quick healthy supper.As part of an Intermittent diet plan, 1 serving provides 2 of your 6 daily vegetable portions.\n This meal provides 205 kcal per portion.\n', 30, 30, 2, 13),
(371, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bananasfoster_85138\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_and_kimchi_bao_75627\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/somerset_chicken_36937\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/somerset_chicken_36937_16x9.jpg\n Slow cooker chicken casserole\n Adding dumplings to this simple, slow-cooker chicken casserole makes it great value when feeding the family.\n Equipment and preparartion: For this recipe you will need a  6.5 litre/11½ pints electric slow-cooker.\n \n', 30, 120, 4, 15),
(372, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/steamed_bass_and_50061\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282bx4.jpg\n', 'Steamed bass and tomatoes with sardine and tomato ketchup\n', ' Try making your own sardine-flavoured ketchup for this delicate steamed fish and tomato dinner for two.\n', 30, 30, 2, 14),
(373, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tarkadal_90055\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tarkadal_90055_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tarka dal\n', ' Cheap, delicious and healthy – dal is the perfect comfort food supper.\n Each serving provides 650 kcal, 30g protein, 77g carbohydrates (of which 9g sugars), 21.5g fat (of which 2g saturates), 14g fibre and 0.7g salt.\n \n', 30, 120, 2, 16),
(374, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pecan_and_maple_63294\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pecan_and_maple_63294_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pecan and maple pinwheels\n', ' Light, flaky Danish pastry topped with pecans, maple syrup and a vanilla icing. \n For this recipe you will need a food processor and a piping bag fitted with a plain nozzle.\n', 120, 120, 12, 18),
(375, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/taglioliniwithlemono_70911\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/taglioliniwithlemono_70911_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tagliatelle with cavolo nero, chickpeas and pecorino\n', ' Quick, easy and healthy. This pasta recipe is on the table in less than 20 minutes.\n Each serving provides 713kcal, 28g protein, 77g carbohydrate (of which 4.5g sugars), 31g fat (of which 8.5g saturates), 8g fibre and 0.5g salt.\n', 30, 10, 4, 11),
(376, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pork_carnitas_with_sweet_06014\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027v8xm.jpg\n', 'Pork carnitas with sweet potato fries and pico de gallo\n', ' This Mexican pulled pork is perfect for a weekend treat with friends. Serve with batata y yuca fritas (sweet potato and cassava fries) to keep things authentic. \n', 120, 120, 4, 23),
(377, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/prune_and_armagnac_tart_36307\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p03c0l0n.jpg\n', 'Prune and Armagnac tart \n', ' Armagnac is a special-occasion tipple, so it’s perfect at Christmas. Try it in this sensational dessert.\n', 90, 90, 8, 13),
(378, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/arroz_verde_49624\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/arroz_verde_49624_16x9.jpg\n', 'Arroz verde\n', ' Bring the flavours of the sea to your table with this dish inspired by Rick Stein\'s trip to Cadiz. \n', 30, 90, 4, 20),
(379, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cowboy_meatballs_35912\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/simple_chicken_curry_09881\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/simple_chicken_curry_09881_16x9.jpg\n', ' Simple chicken and potato curry\n This recipe makes excellent use of a whole chicken. Serve with rice, or if you have time, homemade roti.\n This meal, if served as six portions, provides 491kcal, 59g protein, 27g carbohydrate (of which 6g sugars), 15g fat (of which	3g saturates), 7g fibre and 0.7g salt per portion.\n', 90, 90, 4, 10),
(380, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/apricot_chestnut_and_76988\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/apricot_chestnut_and_76988_16x9.jpg\n', 'Apricot, chestnut and aduki balls with roasted vegetables and white wine miso gravy\n', ' This colourful vegan dish is a fruity, spicy treat with enough wow factor to serve as a main course at a dinner party.\n This meal provides 527 kcal, 18g protein, 87g carbohydrate (of which 37g sugars), 16g fat (of which 10.5g saturates), 33g fibre and 2.5g salt per portion.\n', 30, 120, 4, 23),
(381, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cepstortelliniwithro_93488\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cepstortelliniwithro_93488_16x9.jpg\n', 'Ceps tortellini with roasted nuts and sage butter\n', ' Celebrate ceps with Raymond Blanc\'s delicious tortellini recipe served with a simple sage butter.\n', 90, 30, 4, 15),
(382, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sicilianstylesalmonw_87777\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sicilianstylesalmonw_87777_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sicilian-style salmon with garlic mushrooms\n', ' Bring the flavours of Siciliy to your plate with this simple fish supper. \n', 30, 30, 1, 11),
(383, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_fondants_with_27862\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_fondants_with_27862_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate fondants with almond brittle\n', ' Deceptively simple, this dessert, but it’s utterly thrilling when that first spoonful releases the molten chocolate centre. \n Equipment and preparation: You will need 4 x dariole moulds.\n \n', 30, 30, 4, 8),
(384, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/snowfleckedchocolate_84992\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/snowfleckedchocolate_84992_16x9.jpg\n', 'Double chocolate brownies\n', ' A generous helping of white chocolate in these double chocolate brownies makes them even more irresistible.\n', 30, 30, 20, 8),
(385, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spatchcock_poussins_with_63220\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282c64.jpg\n', 'Spatchcock poussins with orange, sage and ginger\n', ' I love the flavours in this recipe, and have adapted it over the years. A whole poussin is often too much for one person, so I cut them in half once cooked - or you can use chicken breasts or quarters, if you prefer.\n', 480, 90, 6, 12),
(386, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/simple_chicken_curry_46082\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/butternut_squash_soup_90300\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/butternut_squash_soup_90300_16x9.jpg\n', ' Butternut squash soup\n Nothing gets wasted in Nigel Slater\'s butternut squash soup: the crisps that go with this easy soup are made with rosemary-speckled squash peelings. \n', 30, 30, 3, 12),
(387, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/dark_and_white_chocolate_89301\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/dark_and_white_chocolate_89301_16x9.jpg\n', 'Double chocolate cherry brownies\n', ' James Martin\'s easy brownies combine chocolate and decadent cherries for a rich, fruity flavour – just bake and go!\n', 30, 30, 12, 8),
(388, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/strawberry_mousse_56435\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/strawberry_mousse_56435_16x9.jpg\n', 'Strawberry mousse \n', ' End your meal on a high with a deliciously fruity and light strawberry mousse.\n Each serving provides 170 kcal, 2g protein, 18g carbohydrate (of which 18g sugars), 9g fat (of which 5.5g saturates), 3g fibre and 0.1g salt.\n', 120, 30, 6, 7),
(389, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemonricottaandpotat_92836\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vx7p.jpg\n', 'Lemon, ricotta and potato cake\n', ' None\n', 30, 120, 8, 11),
(390, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/peaandspringonioncha_73827\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pasta_rotolo_with_82739\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027w5ns.jpg\n', ' Pasta rotolo with creamed endive \n This is a fiddly dish of homemade pasta wrapped into a Swiss roll shape, stuffed with pork and fennel, but it’s well worth the effort once you try it with creamy chicory on the side.\n Equipment and preparation: you will need a pasta machine and a food processor.\n', 120, 30, 4, 21),
(391, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spelt_risotto_with_69629\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pork_and_potato_hash_76723\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/puff_pastry_pizza_bites_98325\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/puff_pastry_pizza_bites_98325_16x9.jpg\n Puff pastry bites\n Bite-size pizzas with puff pastry bases make perfect party food. Here are two simple topping ideas to try.\n \n', 30, 30, 72, 12),
(392, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/prosciutto_mozzarella_98052\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/prosciutto_mozzarella_98052_16x9.jpg\n', 'Prosciutto, mozzarella and fig pizza\n', ' Once you\'ve mastered Lorraine Pascale\'s basic pizza dough, vary the toppings according to your mood.\n Equipment and preparation: You will need a very large baking tray, or a 30cm/12in pizza plate.\n', 90, 30, 4, 11),
(393, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pepperpotstewwithspi_91703\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Pepperpot stew with spillers dumplings\n', ' None\n', 30, 120, 8, 25),
(394, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow-cooker_roast_ham_25878\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow-cooker_roast_ham_25878_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker honey roast ham  \n', ' How to cook ham in the slow cooker with zero effort. Then get it in the oven, slathered in mustard, honey and sugar, to crisp up. Irresistible.\n Each serving provides 348 kcal, 37g protein, 5g carbohydrates (of which 5g sugars), 20g fat (of which 6.5g saturates), 0g fibre and 4.7g salt.\n', 30, 120, 10, 5),
(395, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/steak_florentine_49943\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fruit_tarts_45402\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fruit_tarts_45402_16x9.jpg\n', ' Fabulous fruit tarts\n These light sweet pastry and crème pâtissière tarts are simple to make and look stunning. Use your own favourite fruits.\n', 120, 30, 12, 18),
(396, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/three-colour_ravioli_91418\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/black_cod_with_steamed_57635\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/whole_roasted_masala_77631\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/whole_roasted_masala_77631_16x9.jpg\n Roast chicken masala and potatoes\n This whole chicken is marinated in spices before being roasted to a juicy, succulent dish served with spicy potatoes.\n Each serving provides 569kcal, 73g protein, 47g carbohydrate (of which 2g sugars),	9 fat (of which 2g saturates), 5g fibre and 1.3g salt.\n', 90, 120, 4, 16),
(397, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_meringues_28772\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_meringues_28772_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan pavlovas\n', ' Vegan meringues are easy to make and require little hands on time. These contain relatively cheap ingredients so you can make them all the time.\n Each serving provides 163 kcal, 1.5g protein, 13g carbohydrates (of which 12g sugars), 12g fat (of which 10g saturates), 0.7g fibre and trace salt. \n', 30, 120, 6, 11),
(398, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemon_sole_with_slow_24057\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027v9wc.jpg\n', 'Lemon sole with slow-cooked leek, brown shrimp and capers\n', ' Cook this simple supper for one in under an hour and add a bit of luxury to your mid-week menu.\n', 30, 90, 1, 14),
(399, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/teriyaki_steak_with_35460\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzn3.jpg\n', 'Teriyaki steak with Asian bean salad\n', ' Bring some Asian flavours to your steak supper with a teriyaki marinade and spicy bean salad.\n', 120, 10, 4, 21),
(400, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/greenchutney_86561\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/greenchutney_86561_16x9.jpg\n', 'Green chutney\n', ' This goes well with all tandoori dishes and most North Indian snacks. It keeps well in the fridge for 4-5 days. You can add yoghurt and a pinch of sugar for a green chutney as you\'d find in restaurants, or add desiccated coconut for a Southern flavour.\n', 30, 0, 200, 11),
(401, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/braised_rabbit_with_62688\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p00z9l6l.jpg\n', 'Braised rabbit with chilli, garlic and artichokes with roasted fennel\n', ' Diced rabbit cooked in a wonderfully flavoured white wine sauce with a dash of chilli heat, served with simply roasted fennel on the side.\n', 30, 120, 4, 12),
(402, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/shepherdspiewithspic_83899\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/shepherdspiewithspic_83899_16x9.jpg\n', 'Nigel Slater\'s shepherd\'s pie with spiced parsnip mash\n', ' Using parsnips instead of potatoes adds a gently sweetness to Nigel Slater\'s brilliant shepherd\'s pie recipe.\n This meal provides 814 kcal, 49g protein, 39g carbohydrate (of which 18.5g sugars), 56g fat (of which 29g saturates), 17g fibre and 1.4g salt per portion.\n', 90, 120, 4, 22),
(403, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/how_to_make_fish_fingers_64484\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/how_to_make_fish_fingers_64484_16x9.jpg\n', 'How to make fish fingers\n', ' Home-made fish fingers have more fish, more flavour and more crunch than shop bought. Well worth the extra effort.\n', 90, 30, 4, 14),
(404, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_pastry_21092\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_pastry_21092_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan pastry \n', ' With just three store cupboard ingredients, you can make this cheap and easy vegan pastry in no time at all.\n This dough provides 949 kcal, 15g protein, 116g carbohydrate (of which 1g sugars), 46g fat (of which 6g saturates), 6g fibre and 2.5g salt.\n', 30, 30, 1, 3),
(405, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/hot_honey_mustard_sauce_76108\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/hot_honey_mustard_sauce_76108_16x9.jpg\n', 'Hot honey mustard sauce\n', ' A sweet and spicy honey mustard sauce you can pair with pork, chicken, veggies, chips or whatever you fancy. \n Click the image to watch five more easy sauces, such as Cajun mayo, burger sauce, \n hot sweet sauce, smoky BBQ and satay dip\n', 30, 0, 1, 6),
(406, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/t-bone_steak_with_38432\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p01lrhsx.jpg\n', 'T-bone steak with bearnaise sauce and a green salad\n', ' This cut of steak is quite expensive, so if you decide to treat yourself you might as well go the whole hog and serve it with some smart trimmings.\n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need a blender and deep-fat fryer.\n', 30, 90, 2, 30),
(407, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/medley_of_mini_sables_84193\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/medley_of_mini_sables_84193_16x9.jpg\n', 'Jammy biscuits\n', ' Small dollops of fruit jam add an extra touch of sweetness to these moreish butter cookies. \n', 30, 30, 4, 7),
