(458, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/how_to_make_thai_green_83259\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/how_to_make_thai_green_83259_16x9.jpg\n', 'Prawn Thai green curry\n', ' This fresh Thai green curry recipe shows you how easy it is to make your own curry paste. Use with prawns, veg or chicken for a brilliantly zingy flavour.\n', 30, 30, 4, 28),
(459, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/wildmushroomrisottow_90966\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p075zb20.jpg\n', 'Wild mushroom risotto with truffle oil\n', ' None\n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(460, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/coffee_panna_cotta_with_85926\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/braisedbeancurdwithg_8815\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mulledwinetrifle_93108\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mulledwinetrifle_93108_16x9.jpg\n Mulled wine trifle\n A trifle for when you want something different. Ginger, cinnamon, cloves and cardamom add festive spice, while a triple threat of vanilla vodka, port and red wine make it extra boozy.\n', 480, 30, 12, 15),
(461, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/dover_sole_with_lime_and_52911\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p017thg3.jpg\n', 'Dover sole with lime and ginger\n', ' Any sweet, meaty white fish, such as hake, cod and John Dory would make a good alternative to Dover sole, or you could try sea bass or bream fillets if you want a lighter option. If you’re using bass or bream you can skip the oven stage, and simply fry them in the pan: start them off skin-side down, then cook for a few minutes on the flesh side.\n', 30, 10, 2, 13),
(462, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lamb_cutlet_in_tandoori_08184\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Lamb cutlet in tandoori spices with pearl barley, greens and raita\n', ' A light and luxurious way to enjoy Indian food. Try it as a weekend treat for two.\n', 90, 30, 2, 27),
(463, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/basictomatoandbasils_67840\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/basictomatoandbasils_67840_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tomato pasta sauce\n', ' This is a really easy pasta sauce recipe - vary the flavour by adding different ingredients (see Top recipe tip below).\n Each serving provides 112kcal, 2.5g protein, 11.5g carbohydrates (of which 11g sugars), 6g fat (of which 0.8g saturates), 2g fibre and trace salt.\n', 30, 90, 6, 11),
(464, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chestnutleekandmushr_66048\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chestnutleekandmushr_66048_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chestnut, leek and mushroom tartlets\n', ' A vegetarian starter or light lunch for the winter. This makes either four individual tartlets with 10cm/4in loose-bottomed flan rings or one larger one using a 20-22cm/8-9in flan ring.\n', 90, 120, 4, 13),
(465, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/queen_of_puddings_33046\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/queen_of_puddings_33046_16x9.jpg\n', 'Nigella\'s queen of puddings \n', ' I wasn’t brought up on nursery food, so this sort of old-fashioned English pudding holds a certain exotic charm for me. Traditionally, a queen of puddings is made with breadcrumbs, but this is the Marie Antoinette version, using brioche instead. \n Equipment: You will need a 1.5 litres/2¾ pints oval pie dish, approx. 28x20x5cm/11x8x2in\n', 30, 90, 6, 13),
(466, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bobotie_83671\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282dg3.jpg\n', 'Bobotie\n', ' None\n', 30, 120, 4, 19),
(467, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_truffle_pot_53461\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_truffle_pot_53461_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate truffle pots\n', ' Mary Berry\'s chocolate truffle pots are perfect who want an after dinner chocolate to last longer. \n', 480, 30, 6, 8),
(468, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/prawn_laksa_rice_noodle_12790\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/doris_grant_loaf_16985\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/doris_grant_loaf_16985_16x9.jpg\n', ' Doris Grant loaf\n This ‘no-need-to-knead bread’ was adapted from a 1940s recipe by healthy-eating evangelist Doris Grant, who believed white flour – and its lack of nutrients – was the enemy. Making bread one day, Doris forgot to knead it. On tasting the loaf, she discovered it had a fair taste and decided never again to bother kneading her bread. The resulting loaf is heavy, but quicker to make than other types of bread.\n', 120, 90, 1, 9),
(469, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/leekandpotatosoupwit_93783\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p074k0t9.jpg\n', 'Leek and potato soup with crisp ox tongue and poached egg\n', ' If you can\'t get ox tongue for this leek and potato soup, substitute with crispy bacon.\n', 30, 120, 4, 15),
(470, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/goats_cheese_red_onion_69475\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027w2bq.jpg\n', 'Goats’ cheese, red onion and caraway seed tart\n', ' Goats’ cheese takes sweetness well, so here we’ve paired it with an onion marmalade cut with balsamic vinegar and some caraway seeds. These flavours work well with any goats’ cheese.\n', 30, 120, 4, 18),
(471, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/peanutbutterfudge_93630\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/peanutbutterfudge_93630_16x9.jpg\n', 'Peanut butter fudge\n', ' Sophie Dahl\'s homemade fudge recipe makes an easy sweet treat or a stunning edible gift.\n', 30, 10, 36, 6),
(472, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/baked_ricotta_and_cream_48552\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/baked_ricotta_and_cream_48552_16x9.jpg\n', 'Baked cheesecake with blackberries, blueberries and  figs \n', ' Previously I have always done no-bake cheesecakes. Partly due to laziness and partly because I was unsure of the taste. But I finally succumbed and this is a stunning cheesecake with so much rich, creamy flavour. I believe I am now a baked cheesecake expert!\n Equipment and preparation: you will need a 23cm/9in springform cake tin.\n \n', 30, 90, 8, 14),
(473, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/irishbeefstew_73826\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/irishbeefstew_73826_16x9.jpg\n', 'Irish stew\n', ' Hearty and wholesome, Rachel Allen\'s slow-cooked beef stew is the ultimate taste of Ireland. \n', 30, 120, 6, 18),
(474, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_pesto_and_rocket_00432\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_pesto_and_rocket_00432_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken, pesto and rocket sandwich\n', ' These sandwiches take no time to make and are great for a school packed lunch.\n Each sandwich provides 347 kcal, 30g protein, 29g carbohydrate (of which 2.2g sugars), 12.5g fat (of which 2.5g saturates), 3g fibre and 1g salt per portion.\n', 30, 0, 6, 6),
(475, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/potato_salad_with_lovage_55317\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/potato_salad_with_lovage_55317_16x9.jpg\n', 'Potato salad with lovage \n', ' Potatoes love lovage: this celery-like garden herb is a match made in heaven with new potatoes.  But you can always use fresh parsley if it\'s not available.\n', 30, 30, 2, 18),
(476, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tangerine_beef_61872\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pickledcucumber_11033\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pickledcucumber_11033_16x9.jpg\n', ' Pickled cucumber\n This quick pickled cucumber recipe is great for serving alongside burgers or in a roast beef sandwich.\n', 120, 0, 4, 6),
(477, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bananabread_74771\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bananabread_74771_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gluten-free banana bread\n', ' Soft, speckled bananas are best for this recipe. The mixture also makes adorable little mini muffins if you cook them in individual cases - great for children\'s packed lunches. Big kids like them too!\n', 30, 120, 1, 11),
(478, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quick_korma_75721\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/quick_korma_75721_16x9.jpg\n', 'Quick veggie korma\n', ' Nigel Slater’s aromatic, creamy korma makes a welcome meal to come home to on a cold night.\n', 30, 30, 4, 19),
(479, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fillet_of_john_dory_with_47202\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sweetandsoursoyporkb_89269\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07pc634.jpg\n', ' Sweet and sour pork buns\n An overnight marinade makes it easy to crank out these Chinese pork buns with their sticky glaze that\'s full of flavour.  \n', 480, 30, 4, 13),
(480, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chilli_sauce_09570\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282bx4.jpg\n', 'Chilli sauce\n', ' Authentic Mexican chillies coupled with cocoa powder, various spices and, rather surprisingly, cola make this simple chilli sauce great for drizzling on Mexican food.\n', 30, 120, 2, 17),
(481, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rolled_lemon_pancakes_83289\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/rolled_lemon_pancakes_83289_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gluten-free pancakes with blueberries and yoghurt\n', ' This delicious gluten-free pancake recipe combine coconut, lemon and blueberry for a lipsmacking dessert that is low in added sugar. \n This meal provides 406 kcal, 13.5g protein, 40g carbohydrate (of which 18g sugars), 21g fat (of which 14g saturates), 7g fibre and 1.1g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(482, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_kiev_with_mash_14334\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_kiev_with_mash_14334_16x9.jpg\n', 'How to make chicken kievs\n', ' This chicken kiev recipe is seriously good. If you enjoy a little heat, add some dried chilli flakes to give a delicious kick.\n', 90, 30, 4, 12),
(483, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_chocolate_birthday_90089\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_chocolate_birthday_90089_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy chocolate birthday cake\n', ' This is a really easy birthday cake for kids of all ages. Dan Lepard shows you how to make it in a step-by-step video. \n', 30, 120, 1, 14),
(484, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/appleandblueberrycob_12556\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vx7p.jpg\n', 'Apple and blueberry cobbler\n', ' None\n', 30, 90, 6, 6),
(485, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/noodles_with_bean_36223\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sweet_red_pepper_and_25318\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sweet_red_pepper_and_25318_16x9.jpg\n', ' Sweet red pepper and tomato soup\n Roasting the peppers, shallots and tomatoes gives this simple soup a lovely rich flavour. \n', 30, 30, 4, 11),
(486, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_spaghetti_bolognese_93639\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_spaghetti_bolognese_93639_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy spaghetti Bolognese\n', ' Everyone needs a basic spaghetti Bolognese recipe that still tastes great, no matter how simple. Get that depth of flavour by cooking the sauce very gently until it’s super rich. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n Each serving provides 787 kcal, 35g protein, 103g carbohydrates (of which 19g sugars), 24g fat (of which 8g saturates), 8.5g fibre and 1.5g salt.\n', 30, 90, 4, 10),
(487, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lime_and_coconut_93553\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lime_and_coconut_93553_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lime and coconut meringue pie\n', ' The traditional lemon meringue pie is given a tropical twist with lime and coconut.\n For this recipe you will need a 20cm/8in loose-bottomed flan tin, a sugar thermometer, a freestanding mixer fitted with a whisk attachment and a large piping bag fitted with a large star nozzle.\n', 90, 120, 1, 17),
(488, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/stuffed_chicken_breasts_14926\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/stuffed_chicken_breasts_14926_16x9.jpg\n', 'Stuffed chicken breasts\n', ' An easy chicken recipe for two that won’t fail to impress. Serve with steamed new potatoes for a bigger meal.\n', 30, 30, 2, 15),
(489, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_spanish_chicken_09987\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_spanish_chicken_09987_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy Spanish chicken \n', ' This satisfying and tasty meal is also surprisingly healthy and is suitable as a dinner for anyone following a diet of 1200–1500 calories a day. \n With a GI of 58 this meal is high protein, low GI.\n \n Each serving provides 352 kcal, 32g protein, 8.5g carbohydrates (of which 10.5g sugars), 13g fat (of which 4g saturates), 9g fibre and 1.7g salt. \n \n \n With a GI of 58 this meal is high protein, low GI.\n', 30, 30, 4, 17),
(490, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastedseabasswithch_85255\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastedseabasswithch_85255_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roasted sea bass with chorizo, red onion and cherry tomatoes\n', ' James Martin\'s stylish sea bass recipe is ready in under half an hour.\n', 30, 30, 4, 13),
(491, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_lemon_drizzle_81528\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_lemon_drizzle_81528_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan lemon drizzle cake\n', ' The lemon juice and sugar poured over while the cake is still warm gives a lovely sugary citrus topping to this easy vegan lemon cake. \n You will need 1 x 20cm/8in round cake tin. \n', 30, 120, 8, 10),
(492, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cauliflower_popcorn_12307\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cauliflower_popcorn_12307_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cauliflower ‘popcorn’\n', ' Crisp, garlicky and moreish, these florets of cauliflower dipped in cheesy breadcrumbs make a great snack in front of your favourite movie.\n', 30, 90, 6, 14);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(493, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/french_toast_with_52720\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/french_toast_with_52720_16x9.jpg\n', 'French toast\n', ' French toast is an irresistible all-time favourite weekend breakfast with no health benefits whatsoever. Allegra walks you through the process. Gorgeous.\n', 30, 30, 2, 8),
(494, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bean_chilli_with_43184\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bean_chilli_with_43184_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bean chilli with jackfruit\n', ' This vegan bean chilli contains jackfruit, a delicious fruit that mimics the texture of pulled pork. It\'s easy to make and perfect for feeding a crowd. \n Each serving provides 231 kcal, 24.5g protein, 39g carbohydrates (of which 24.5g sugars), 2.2g fat (of which 1.5g saturates), 9g fibre and 0.3g salt. \n', 30, 90, 8, 20),
(495, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/instant_souffl_with_94231\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p01tlcrc.jpg\n', 'Instant soufflé with caramelised bananas\n', ' Soufflés have a reputation for being difficult but James Martin shows you the cheat’s way to perfect results every time.\n', 30, 30, 4, 9),
(496, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/singaporestylenoodle_89281\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/singaporestylenoodle_89281_16x9.jpg\n', 'Singapore-style noodles\n', ' Make this takeaway favourite at home with our quick and easy Singapore noodle recipe.\n', 30, 10, 2, 19),
(497, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_cooker_roast_22820\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow_cooker_roast_22820_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker roast chicken\n', ' Cooking a whole chicken in a slow cooker keeps it tender and moist. Serve with all the trimmings for an easy Sunday lunch. \n', 30, 120, 4, 9),
(498, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/irishcreambreadandbu_90971\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ultimate_burger_in_a_73911\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/ultimate_burger_in_a_73911_16x9.jpg\n', ' Ultimate burger in a brioche bun\n James Martin once worked in one of the oldest diners in America, so he\'s well-placed to judge what makes the ultimate burger recipe.\n', 120, 10, 4, 17),
(499, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickenlimeandcashew_4133\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chickenlimeandcashew_4133_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken and cashew noodle stir-fry\n', ' A quick, easy and healthy chicken and cashew stir-fry.\n Each serving provides 424 kcal, 28g protein, 39g carbohydrate (of which 11g sugars), 16g fat (of which 2g saturates), 5g fibre and 1g salt.\n', 30, 90, 3, 17),
(500, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tonkatsu_pork_20288\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tonkatsu_pork_20288_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tonkatsu pork\n', ' Breaded pork comes with a sauce made from tomato ketchup and the fire of ginger and mustard in this easy Japanese recipe.\n', 30, 30, 4, 20),
(501, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/citrus_spiced_salmon_69209\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/citrus_spiced_salmon_69209_16x9.jpg\n', 'Citrus spiced salmon\n', ' Sumac and dried lime powder pack a citrus punch that will brighten any piece of fish. Serve with a fattoush salad or Persian herb rice - or both.\n', 30, 30, 4, 12),
(502, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bakedpennewithricott_91319\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bakedpennewithricott_91319_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sausage and ricotta pasta bake\n', ' Looking for wholesome student food? This hearty pasta bake is easy on the wallet and is great for feeding a hungry family too.\n', 30, 30, 4, 11),
(503, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pasta_with_chilli_bacon_13839\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pasta_with_chilli_bacon_13839_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pasta with chilli, bacon and tomato sauce\n', ' This spicy, richly flavoured pasta dish is super quick to make. Use pancetta if you can’t find the cured pork cheeks.\n', 30, 30, 4, 8),
(504, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/classicmojito_72225\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/keralakingprawnandco_75325\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/keralakingprawnandco_75325_16x9.jpg\n', ' Kerala king prawn and coconut curry\n This quick prawn curry is the perfect blend of spicy, fresh and creamy. And it takes minutes to make.\n', 30, 30, 4, 16),
(505, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bacon_and_kale_pasta_28231\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bacon_and_kale_pasta_28231_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bacon and kale pasta\n', ' A tasty protein-packed, high-fibre bacon pasta dish that’s ready in no time.\n Each serving provides 532 kcal, 27g protein, 49g carbohydrate (of which 4g sugars), 23g fat (of which 9g saturates), 10g fibre and 1.9g salt.\n', 30, 30, 4, 10),
(506, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sticky_chicken_and_13331\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sticky_chicken_and_13331_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sticky chicken and vegetable kebabs with couscous\n', ' These sticky chicken kebabs are a real treat and full of tasty veggies to get you on your way to five a day. Serve with couscous for a special supper on a budget. \n Each serving provides 594kcal, 41g protein, 72g carbohydrate (of which 17g sugars), 14g fat (of which 2g saturates), 6.5g fibre and	1.4g salt.\n \n Try the Eat Well for Less quiz to find out how you could cut your food bills. \n \n (For this recipe you will need 10 skewers to make the kebabs. Or just roast the ingredients on the baking trays without the skewers.)\n \n \n \n \n', 120, 90, 5, 16),
(507, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/stuffin_muffins_60231\n', 'None\n', 'Stuffin\' muffins\n', ' Lucky enough to have leftover stuffing? Skip the sandwiches and transform it into a brilliant Boxing Day breakfast. \n', 30, 30, 6, 8),
(508, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ovenfriedchillichick_86437\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/ovenfriedchillichick_86437_16x9.jpg\n', 'Oven-fried chilli chicken\n', ' Lightly spiced, crispy chicken pieces baked in the oven, rather than fried, to reduce those pesky calories.\n', 480, 90, 6, 16),
(509, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roti_31237\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roti_31237_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roti\n', ' An authentic roti bread recipe, brilliant to serve with curries, making a good alternative to rice.\n', 90, 30, 6, 4),
(510, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sweet_and_sour_pork_with_22016\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sweet_and_sour_pork_with_22016_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sweet and sour pork stir-fry\n', ' This sweet and sour pork recipe is easier than picking up a phone. Use a packet of ready-cooked rice for the egg fried rice.\n', 30, 90, 4, 20),
