(632, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lobster_with_garlic_36735\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tiramisu_cake_13686\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tiramisu_cake_13686_16x9.jpg\n', ' Tiramisu cake\n Like Mary Berry herself, this version of tiramisu is elegant, generous and very sweet. \n Equipment and preparation: You will need a 38x25cm/15x10in Swiss roll tin, a 18cm/7in square tin and a cook\'s thermometer.\n', 30, 120, 9, 12),
(633, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/toad_in_the_hole_with_42100\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/turkey_ham_and_stuffing_59799\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/turkey_ham_and_stuffing_59799_16x9.jpg\n', ' Turkey, ham and stuffing pie\n The Hairy Bikers\' delicious turkey pie uses up your Christmas turkey and leftovers. It\'s a really creamy pie, made with leeks, tarragon and homemade pastry.\n', 90, 120, 6, 17),
(634, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/originalcremebrulee_81524\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/originalcremebrulee_81524_16x9.jpg\n', 'Original crème brûlée\n', ' These vanilla-rich puds are deliciously decadent. If you don’t own a mini blowtorch, caramelise them under the grill.\n', 30, 30, 6, 4),
