(724, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smoked_mackerel_pilau_66783\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smoked_mackerel_pilau_66783_16x9.jpg\n', 'Smoked mackerel pilau rice\n', ' This is a great one-pan family meal that’s tasty and healthy too. If you like more spice, add some ginger and chilli to the vegetables at the start. You can also add boiled eggs at the end too bulk it out.\n Each serving provides 430 kcal, 18g protein, 56g carbohydrates (of which 3g sugars), 14g fat (of which 3g saturates), 4g fibre and 1g salt.\n', 30, 90, 4, 14),
(725, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/coconut_prawn_curry_69561\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/coconut_prawn_curry_69561_16x9.jpg\n', 'Prawns with coconut, chillies and mustard seeds \n', ' This is a popular dish in Bengal, where of course both prawns and coconut abound. It’s normally served in a whole green coconut there, but that’s a bridge too far for us. I would suggest serving it, as in Bengal, as a little course in its own right, but it’s also delicious with some rice and flatbreads.\n', 30, 30, 4, 10),
(726, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/raspberry_cinnamon_60820\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/raspberry_cinnamon_60820_16x9.jpg\n', 'Raspberry cinnamon meringue\n', ' Light, crisp balls of meringue topped with raspberries and dark chocolate.\n', 30, 90, 8, 5),
(727, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/layered_beef_and_36022\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p017j48p.jpg\n', 'Layered beef and mushroom suet pudding\n', ' Come in from the cold with this comforting steamed pudding of beef, stout and mushrooms. Look for well-marbled braising beef such as chuck steak for this recipe.\n', 90, 120, 6, 19),
(728, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pimms_lollies_94967\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pimms_lollies_94967_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pimms ice lollies\n', ' Serve these naughty Pimms lollies instead of dessert at a summer barbecue. \n Equipment: for this recipe you will need wooden lolly sticks and lolly moulds.\n', 120, 0, 10, 6),
(729, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_and_blue_cheese_34718\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/warm_salmon_salad_13819\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/warm_salmon_salad_13819_16x9.jpg\n', ' Warm crispy salmon salad\n A bright, crisp veg-packed salad with salmon that would make a lovely light summer supper when you have friends over. \n Each serving provides 696 kcal, 48g protein, 18g carbohydrates (of which 6g sugars), 46g fat (of which 8g saturates), 12g fibre and 0.3g salt.\n', 30, 30, 4, 16),
(730, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pork_chops_two_ways_54107\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pork_chops_two_ways_54107_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pork chops two ways\n', ' This recipe makes two meals for adults and two meals for children. The pork is sliced and added to a wrap for the kid’s tea, and a whole pork chop is marinated for the grown-ups to have later with a baked potato and salad.\n', 30, 90, 4, 16),
(731, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/raspberry_lighter_49494\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/raspberry_lighter_49494_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate log\n', ' This chocolate Swiss roll is our easier and lighter version of a Christmas Yule log. It is the perfect way to finish off a festive feast. \n', 30, 30, 10, 8),
(732, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/altcrustchickenwithp_88912\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Salt crust chicken with peas, broad beans and mousseron mushrooms\n', ' Cook your chicken inside a salt crust for the juiciest, moistest roast chicken you can imagine. Serving it with a pea, mushroom and broad bean sauce is gilding the lily, but why not?\n', 120, 90, 2, 24),
(733, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/classicsummerberryso_70045\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/classicsummerberryso_70045_16x9.jpg\n', 'Classic summer berry sorbet\n', ' This refreshing super-smooth sorbet makes great use of all the wonderful summer fruits that are now in abundance.\n', 120, 0, 6, 6),
(734, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/stuffedportabellamus_85840\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/stuffedportabellamus_85840_16x9.jpg\n', 'Stuffed Portobello mushrooms with blue cheese \n', ' An easy starter for dinner parties or a simple meal for one served with some fresh crusty bread to mop up the juices.\n', 30, 30, 1, 11),
(735, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beefbourguignon_5151\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beefbourguignon_5151_16x9.jpg\n', 'Best beef bourguignon\n', ' Rich and rib-sticking, Antony Worrall Thompson’s slow-cooked beef bourguignon is well worth the wait.\n Each serving provides 845 kcal, 68g protein, 13g carbohydrates (of which 7g sugars), 33g fat (of which 13.5g saturates), 4.5g fibre and 1.8g salt.\n', 480, 120, 6, 20),
(736, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roast_monkfish_with_70770\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roast_monkfish_with_70770_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roast monkfish with cumin and coriander\n', ' This is a very simple recipe with a piece of lightly spiced monkfish on a bed of aubergine purée served with a sharp, slightly spicy dressing.\n', 480, 120, 2, 16),
(737, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/warm_spiced_cauliflower_36652\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/warm_spiced_cauliflower_36652_16x9.jpg\n', 'Warm spiced cauliflower and chickpea salad with pomegranate seeds\n', ' This is one of my favourite suppers, although there’s nothing that says you can’t serve this as a vegetable side. And you could also bolster it further by crumbling in some feta. But for me, it is perfect just as it is.\n', 30, 30, 2, 12),
(738, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/keylimepie_93185\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/keylimepie_93185_16x9.jpg\n', 'Key lime pie\n', ' This classic American dessert is sure to impress, perfect when you want something different for a dinner party!\n', 120, 30, 8, 12),
(739, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/honey_mustard_beetroot_96264\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cranachan_20683\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cranachan_20683_16x9.jpg\n', ' Lighter cranachan\n This recipe is based on a traditional Scottish cranachan but with the addition of half-fat crème fraiche to lighten the cream mixture and some flaked almonds for extra crunch. \n', 30, 10, 6, 9),
(740, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/porcini_nut_patties_99470\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/porcini_nut_patties_99470_16x9.jpg\n', 'Porcini nut patties\n', ' Nut roast doesn\'t have to be dry, leaden or worthy. These little patties have juicy, rich mushrooms and tasty macadamia nuts.\n This meal, when served as 15 portions, provides 267kcal, 6g protein, 18g carbohydrates (of which 5g sugars), 18g fat (of which 1.5g saturates), 3.5g fibre and 0.4g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 10, 12),
(741, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tomatotagliatelle_90689\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p075zb20.jpg\n', 'Tomato tagliatelle\n', ' None\n', 30, 30, 1, 9),
(742, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cholent_16734\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cholent_16734_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cholent\n', ' A classic Jewish recipe, cholent is traditionally cooked overnight on a Friday and eaten for lunch on the Sabbath.\n', 90, 120, 6, 13),
(743, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pea_and_pancetta_soup_82240\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pea_and_pancetta_soup_82240_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pea soup with pancetta\n', ' Nigel Slater makes his simple pea soup recipe next-level with crisp, fried pancetta. So simple, but classy enough to serve as a dinner party starter.\n Each serving provides 242kcal, 21g protein, 14.5g carbohydrate (of which 3.5g sugars), 10g fat (of which 4	6 saturates), 5g fibre and 1.6g salt.\n', 30, 10, 4, 5),
(744, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/freshmackerelwithroa_92281\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/freshmackerelwithroa_92281_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fresh mackerel with roasted rhubarb\n', ' Believe it or not, this is a classic combination. Tart rhubarb cuts through the richness of smoky, oily mackerel for a perfect spring supper.\n', 30, 30, 2, 9),
(745, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/nut_roast_74357\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/nut_roast_74357_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy nut roast\n', ' This really easy vegetarian nut roast can happily be made in advance and sit for a half an hour. It’s also brilliant cold with chutney in sandwiches.\n', 30, 120, 10, 25),
(746, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/five-spice_braised_beef_86835\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/five-spice_braised_beef_86835_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker Chinese-style beef\n', ' This slow-cooker beef recipe makes a lovely change from a stir-fry but is just as easy to prepare. \n Equipment and preparation: For this recipe, you will need an electric slow-cooker, at least 3.5 litres/6 pints in capacity. \n \n', 30, 120, 4, 12),
(747, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pear_tart_with_stilton_36656\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pear_tart_with_stilton_36656_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pear tart with Stilton and pistachios\n', ' You could cook the pastry and pears well in advance and assemble these gorgeous veggie tarts in 5 minutes.\n', 30, 120, 4, 14),
(748, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/baba_ganoush_44415\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/baba_ganoush_44415_16x9.jpg\n', 'Baba ganoush\n', ' A delicious smoky aubergine dip. Try it with a Middle-Eastern flatbread such as maneesh. \n', 30, 30, 6, 7);
