(983, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_and_pork_meatballs_23514\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beef_and_pork_meatballs_23514_16x9.jpg\n', 'Meatballs in a spicy tomato sauce (Boles de picolat)\n', ' This recipe came from a stall in Prades market where they were cooking boles meatballs in a huge paella pan. They were fabulous – beef and pork meatballs flavoured with cinnamon and piment d’Espelette in an exquisite tomato sauce with green olives, haricot beans and bacon. I thought there might be too much meat in the dish, but not at all.\n', 30, 120, 4, 20),
(984, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/anything-goes_frittata_95480\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/anything-goes_frittata_95480_16x9.jpg\n', 'Anything-goes frittata\n', ' This frittata recipe is super flexible. You can use just about anything that\'s leftover in the fridge.  \n Each serving provides 337 kcal, 21g protein, 15g carbohydrates (of which 5g sugars), 21g fat (of which 7g saturates), 4.5g fibre and 1g salt.\n', 30, 30, 4, 13),
(985, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smoked_trout_pate_87163\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/peanut_butter_clairs_72663\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027w3lt.jpg\n', ' Peanut butter éclairs\n Chocolate choux pastry filled with peanut butter cream and strawberry jam - a Franco-American fusion that\'s sure to make an impact.\n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need, four piping bags, 15mm plain and star nozzle, a 5mm round nozzle, a 15mm wide ribbon nozzle and a cook\'s thermometer.\n', 120, 90, 12, 19),
(986, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/madeleine_15211\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/madeleine_15211_16x9.jpg\n', 'Madeleines\n', ' Bake a batch of these buttery little French cakes to have with a cup of tea or coffee.\n Equipment and preparation: You will need a 12-cup madeleine tray. \n', 30, 90, 12, 8),
(987, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spatchcock_pigeon_on_60212\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282c64.jpg\n', 'Spatchcock pigeon on sourdough\n', ' This squab pigeon recipe is sure to impress any dinner party guest. \n', 120, 90, 4, 13),
(988, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/kofte_burgers_89900\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/kofte_burgers_89900_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan kofte burgers \n', ' These vegan chickpea burgers freeze well for up to four weeks. Simply wrap each uncooked burger in foil and place in a freezer bag. Cook from frozen, adding an extra 2 minutes on each side.\n Each serving provides 450 kcal, 20g protein, 48g carbohydrates (of which 2.5g sugars), 16.5g fat (of which 2.5g saturates), 13g fibre and 2.2g salt.\n \n', 30, 10, 4, 19),
(989, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vietnamesescallopswi_91368\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzn3.jpg\n', 'Vietnamese-style scallops with papaya salad\n', ' None\n', 30, 10, 4, 17),
(990, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/asian-style_sticky_23400\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/asian-style_sticky_23400_16x9.jpg\n', 'Asian-style sticky chicken\n', ' This simple sticky chicken recipe from Eat Well for Less is a quick crowd-pleaser that the whole family will love. Serve with freshly steamed rice and vegetables.\n Each serving provides 441 kcal, 64g protein, 16g carbohydrate (of which 15g sugars), 13g fat (of which 3g saturates), 0.7g fibre and 2.3g salt.\n', 30, 30, 2, 10),
(991, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fennel_and_feta_linguini_59137\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fennel_and_feta_linguini_59137_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fennel and feta linguine\n', ' A light fresh dish, full of sweet fried flavour - makes a great weeknight dinner.\n', 30, 30, 2, 6),
(992, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/hashbrowns_12454\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/hashbrowns_12454_16x9.jpg\n', 'Hash browns\n', ' Hash browns are one of those brilliant recipes that taste amazing, look impressive and take very little effort. A welcome addition to any breakfast or lunch.\n', 90, 30, 8, 7),
(993, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/yoghurt_and_muesli_61842\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/golden_egg_curry_00708\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/golden_egg_curry_00708_16x9.jpg\n', ' Golden egg curry\n This magnificent addition to my eating life comes courtesy of Yasmin Othman (who has brought much deliciousness my way over the years) and I glow with gratitude every time I eat it. This – called masak lemak telur in Malaysian – is very far removed from the egg curries I remember from my early youth, and would much prefer to forget. What we have here are eggs poached in a rich, aromatic, turmeric-tinted, tamarind-sharp, coconutty sauce or soup. \n', 30, 30, 2, 16),
(994, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smashed_avocado_on_toast_89082\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smashed_avocado_on_toast_89082_16x9.jpg\n', 'Smashed avocado on toast\n', ' So simple and delicious, this is perfect when you need a quick and nutritious breakfast or snack. \n', 30, 0, 1, 9),
(995, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spaghetti_carbonara_95514\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07f3ykj.jpg\n', 'Spaghetti carbonara with garlic bread\n', ' Carbonara is a great way to feed four people quickly. If you have a little time to prepare ahead, then go for the homemade garlic bread too, served warm, straight from the oven!\n', 120, 30, 4, 11),
(996, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_hummus_96922\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_hummus_96922_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy hummus \n', ' No tahini or food processor? No problem! This quick and simple hummus recipe uses peanut butter and a potato masher instead! Serve with warm pitta bread, veggie sticks or tortilla chips for dipping. See also our easy chickpea stew recipe and easy falafel recipe for more ways to shuzsh up that tin!\n', 30, 0, 2, 9),
(997, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/porkchopwithbraisedb_85428\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p017tg7c.jpg\n', 'Pork chop with braised Brussels sprouts, chestnut, red onion and sage\n', ' None\n', 30, 30, 4, 10),
(998, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/baked_samosas_69255\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/baked_samosas_69255_16x9.jpg\n', 'Baked samosas\n', ' Baked samosas are a healthier alternative to the fried versions you find in most Indian takeaways - Manju Mahli’s spicy vegetarian version makes a stunning starter or snack.\n Each serving provides 133kcal, 4g protein, 21g carbohydrate (of which 2g sugars), 3g fat (of which 0.5g saturates), 4g fibre and 0.4g salt.\n', 90, 90, 12, 15);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(999, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/how_to_make_pizza_50967\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/how_to_make_pizza_50967_16x9.jpg\n', 'How to make pizza dough\n', ' Making your own pizza base is easier than you think. The great thing about this pizza dough is that it can be made in advance, and even frozen. If cooking on a budget try cheap toppings such as mushrooms, tinned sweetcorn, onions and peppers.\n Each serving provides 1095 kcal, 31g protein, 190g carbohydrates (of which 2g sugars), 22g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 8g fibre and 5g salt.\n', 30, 120, 2, 9),
(1000, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/saffroncake_91341\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02828qx.jpg\n', 'Saffron cake\n', ' A Cornish classic, perfect for tea time served with a generous smear of clotted cream.\n', 120, 90, 1, 10),
(1001, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/moroccan_lamb_burgers_01067\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegetarianchilli_6544\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegetarianchilli_6544_16x9.jpg\n', ' Vegetarian chilli\n This tasty vegetarian chilli is packed with lentils, veggies and beans. Serve with rice and guacamole, and top with soured cream,  cheese, coriander, fresh chillies...  the list goes on!\n Each serving provides 265kcal, 15g protein, 33g carbohydrate (of which 12g sugars), 5g fat (of which 1g saturates), 12g fibre and 0.4g salt.\n', 90, 90, 4, 16),
(1002, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cardamom_and_lemon_74033\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cardamom_and_lemon_74033_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cardamom and lemon cookies\n', ' We discovered that cardamom is a really popular spice in Norway, used in many cake and biscuit recipes. Some say the spice was first brought back to the country hundreds of years ago by Vikings who worked as mercenaries in what was then Constantinople (now Istanbul). Whatever the truth, Norwegians are certainly keen on their cardamom.We made these cookies on a boat on the Geiranger Fjord – a stunning spot.\n', 90, 30, 24, 7),
(1003, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tandoori_cod_burger_93602\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tandoori_cod_burger_93602_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tandoori cod burger\n', ' Nadiya\'s tandoori fish burger is flavoured with a masala mix and served with a zingy onion and cucumber salad, all sandwiched between slices of brioche. \n', 30, 30, 2, 10),
(1004, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/filletsofsolewrapped_90825\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Sole wrapped in prosciutto with bay leaf sauce (Sogliola al prosciutto crudo in salsa d\'alloro)\n', ' An easy and impressive way to cook lemon sole.\n', 30, 30, 4, 15),
(1005, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/white_radish_salad_90778\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p01tlnvb.jpg\n', 'White radish salad (Sangchae)\n', ' If you can get hold of mouli and the fabulous Korean ingredients for this recipe, you won’t be disappointed with this stunning salad.\n', 30, 0, 4, 12),
(1006, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_pizza_17725\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_pizza_17725_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan pizza \n', ' You can use any vegetables you like for this vegan pizza –  just remember to keep them thinly sliced and don’t overcrowd the base.\n Each serving provides 418 kcal, 13g protein, 47g carbohydrate (of which 8.5g sugars), 19g fat (of which 2g saturates), 6g fibre and 1.9g salt.\n \n', 120, 30, 4, 18),
(1007, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushroom_stroganoff_80260\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mushroom_stroganoff_80260_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mushroom stroganoff\n', ' Try this quick, creamy and comforting vegetarian casserole with brown or basmati rice.\n', 30, 30, 4, 13),
(1008, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_cooker_chilli_con_13029\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow_cooker_chilli_con_13029_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker chilli con carne \n', ' Chocolate added at the end gives a richness to this slow-cooked chilli. You can store any leftovers in the freezer for 2 months. Try it with soured cream, fluffy rice and a scoop of guacamole.\n', 30, 120, 6, 17),
(1009, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/homemadeporksausages_85815\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/basicpancakeswithsuga_66226\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/basicpancakeswithsuga_66226_16x9.jpg\n', ' Pancakes\n Trust Delia Smith to show you how to make the perfect pancake recipe – and enjoy Pancake Day without any flops.\n Once you\'ve mastered how to make Delia\'s pancakes, read our guide for more easy pancake ideas.\n \n Each pancake provides 88kcal, 7.5g carbohydrates (of which 0.9g sugars), 5g fat (of which 2g saturates), 0.4g fibre and 0.2g salt. \n (Not including the lemon and sugar topping)\n', 30, 10, 12, 8),
(1010, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spaghettibolognese_89200\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spaghettibolognese_89200_16x9.jpg\n', 'Nigel Slater\'s spaghetti bolognese\n', ' Make a big batch of Nigel\'s classic bolognese recipe and stash half in the freezer for a quick supper.\n', 30, 120, 4, 18),
(1011, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fraisier_cake_75507\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fraisier_cake_75507_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fraisier cake\n', ' An incredibly pretty French cake filled with delicious strawberries and crème pâtissière. Tricky to achieve but certain to impress.\n', 30, 120, 1, 16),
(1012, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/stickygingerbreadpud_67342\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/stickygingerbreadpud_67342_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sticky gingerbread puddings with ginger wine and brandy sauce\n', ' If you want to make these puddings in advance, they freeze beautifully, and after defrosting should be re-heated as below.\n Equipment and preparation: You will also need eight 175ml/6fl oz  pudding basins, well buttered, and a solid baking sheet.\n', 30, 90, 8, 17),
(1013, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicy_chilli_con_carne_58238\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spicy_chilli_con_carne_58238_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spicy chilli con carne with guacamole\n', ' This easy chilli is enlivened by a salsa crammed with healthy vegetables and creamy avocado. The spiciness can be adjusted to suit your taste.\n This meal provides 393 kcal, 30g protein, 12g carbohydrate (of which 10g sugars), 23g fat (of which 7g saturates), 4g fibre and 0.4g salt per portion.\n', 30, 90, 4, 21),
(1014, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/souped_up_instant_ramen_69512\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/souped_up_instant_ramen_69512_16x9.jpg\n', 'Souped up instant ramen \n', ' Turn a pack of instant noodles into something glorious with a few simple additions - a marinated egg, roast meat, greens and a little mirin if you have it.\n', 30, 10, 1, 12),
(1015, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/goat_koftas_with_a_89880\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Goat koftas with a yoghurt, mint and lime dressing\n', ' This speedy kofta recipe is packed with flavour and would make a great alternative to homemade burgers. Try it with lamb instead of goat meat if you prefer.\n', 30, 10, 4, 19),
(1016, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/eggfriedrice_89260\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/eggfriedrice_89260_16x9.jpg\n', 'Egg fried rice with tomatoes\n', ' This classic Chinese dish is fast, easy and vegetarian. It’s also a tasty way to use up leftovers, especially cold rice.\n', 30, 30, 4, 10),
(1017, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/italcarrotandsweetpo_91711\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vymn.jpg\n', 'Carrot and sweet potato soup\n', ' This sweet and spicy carrot and sweet potato soup is a classic ital recipe – food celebrated by Rastafarians. It\'s a real treat and the main ingredients are really cheap – great for your packed lunch.\n', 30, 30, 4, 17),
(1018, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/flourlesschocolateca_82362\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p076mwwq.jpg\n', 'Rich flourless chocolate cake\n', ' This dish is delicious served with vanilla or pistachio ice cream.\n', 30, 30, 1, 4),
(1019, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_cooked_lamb_26033\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow_cooked_lamb_26033_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow-cooked lamb shoulder\n', ' This is a great dish to cook when you have guests for Sunday lunch – just stick it in the oven and forget about it. The slow cook allows the meat to tenderise slowly and evenly, and you could cook it for even longer than the recipe states if you prefer.\n', 30, 120, 4, 10),
(1020, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/plumandalmondtart_86705\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/plumandalmondtart_86705_16x9.jpg\n', 'Plum and almond tart\n', ' Juicy plums and almonds are a match made in heaven in this delicious pud.\n', 90, 90, 10, 10),
(1021, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pumpkin_soup_with_28693\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicy_tuna_tomato_and_09254\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spicy_tuna_tomato_and_09254_16x9.jpg\n', ' Spicy tuna, tomato and olive pasta\n Spice up your pasta with a little chilli, adding tuna also makes this dish extra filling.\n With a GI of 44, this meal is high protein, low GI and provides 456 kcal per portion.\n', 30, 30, 4, 11),
(1022, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/braisedsavoycabbagew_68087\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/braisedsavoycabbagew_68087_16x9.jpg\n', 'Braised cabbage with bacon\n', ' Braised cabbage elevated to new heights of deliciousness - cooked in wine and cream with salty bacon. Use bright Savoy cabbage, or even cavolo nero!\n', 30, 30, 6, 8),
(1023, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sticky_toffee_pudding_33586\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/singapore_noodles_81196\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/singapore_noodles_81196_16x9.jpg\n', ' Ken Hom\'s Singapore noodles\n Singapore noodles are a delicious and easy dinner option made with store cupboard staples.\n It’s all in the preparation. Soften the super thin noodles before cooking up a fast stir-fry feast.\n', 30, 10, 4, 23),
(1024, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/low-fat_beef_and_bean_53274\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/low-fat_beef_and_bean_53274_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beef and bean burrito\n', ' This healthy beef burrito recipe cuts out most of the fat associated with Mexican food, but there\'s no compromise on flavour.\n This meal provides 434 kcal, 36g protein, 53g carbohydrate (of which 11g sugars), 9g fat (of which 2.7g saturates), 11.5g fibre and 1.1g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 3, 20),
(1025, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/three_ways_with_puff_29378\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chilli_fish_with_tahini_32948\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/braised_beef_with_stout_47057\n', ' https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/paul_hollywoods_scones_70005\n https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/paul_hollywoods_scones_70005_16x9.jpg\n Paul Hollywood\'s scones\n A simple recipe for soft and fluffy scones that are perfect with jam and plenty of clotted cream. \n', 30, 30, 8, 12),
(1026, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/noodlesalad_81382\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027v9wc.jpg\n', 'Noodle salad\n', ' This is the kind of noodle salad you make for lunch out of the store cupboard. Please your mum and add any veg you have.\n', 30, 10, 1, 12),
(1027, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quickapricotappleand_67261\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/quickapricotappleand_67261_16x9.jpg\n', 'Quick apricot, apple and pecan loaf cake\n', ' Delia walks you through this simple tea bread recipe for delicious results - perfect for beginners and for baking with kids.\n Equipment and peparation: You will need one pleated bread loaf tin 900g/2lb with a base measurement of 9x16cm/3½x6½in lightly buttered.\n', 30, 120, 1, 14),
(1028, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_pasta_bake_67249\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_pasta_bake_67249_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan pasta bake\n', ' A vegan mac and cheese that is ridiculously easy to make from the Doctor\'s Kitchen. This pasta bake\'s full of nutritious veg and completely dairy-free.\n Each serving provides 353 kcal, 17g protein, 42g carbohydrates (of which 10.5g sugars), 10.5g fat (of which 1g saturates), 10g fibre and 0.1g salt.\n', 30, 90, 4, 12),
(1029, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/french_dip_sandwich_25385\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quick_orange_and_lemon_60372\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/quick_orange_and_lemon_60372_16x9.jpg\n', ' Quick Chinese citrus chicken stir-fry\n Orange and lemon zest give a zingy flavour to this chicken stir fry, served with garlicky Chinese greens and rice.\n', 30, 30, 4, 17),
(1030, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/grilled_black_truffle_17482\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_mornay_with_01138\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/everyday_roast_chicken_91003\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/everyday_roast_chicken_91003_16x9.jpg\n Everyday roast chicken\n Nigel Slater demonstrates how roast chicken is not just for Sundays with this aromatic and straightforward recipe.\n', 30, 90, 2, 6),
(1031, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lentil_and_tomato_soup_19393\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lentil_and_tomato_soup_19393_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lentil and tomato soup \n', ' A filling and hearty lentil and tomato soup that is packed with fibre and provides two of your five-a-day. Why not make double and freeze for future vegan lunches?\n Each serving provides 200 kcal, 10g protein, 29g carbohydrate (of which 12.5g sugars), 4g fat (of which 05.g saturates), 5g fibre and 0.3g salt.\n', 30, 30, 1, 8),
(1032, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/gingerbread_pancakes_89406\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/gingerbread_pancakes_89406_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gingerbread pancakes\n', ' Major brownie points are awarded to those who go the extra mile on a Sunday and rustle up these delicious gingerbread pancakes. \n If you prefer to have the pancakes plain, then just omit the cinnamon, ground ginger, lemon zest, vanilla and sugar. \n', 30, 30, 4, 16),
(1033, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pembrokeshire_seafood_29704\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pembrokeshire_seafood_29704_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pembrokeshire seafood\n', ' Clams and mussels are served in a creamy sauce topped with seaweed - one to try after a seaside foraging trip. \n', 30, 30, 2, 14),
