(1086, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sweet_onions_with_lentil_01078\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sweet_onions_with_lentil_01078_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lentil stew with sweet onions\n', ' This lentil stew is so comforting – the warm spices are given a delicious lift by the mouth-watering, sweet caramelised onions.\n This meal provides 471 kcal, 25g protein, 51g carbohydrate (of which 13.5g sugars), 19g fat (of which 10.5g saturates), 14g fibre and 1.5g salt per portion.\n', 30, 90, 4, 11),
(1087, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/thai_chicken_pie_20300\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/thai_chicken_pie_20300_16x9.jpg\n', 'Thai chicken pie\n', ' I love a good Thai chicken curry, fragrant with spices, chilli and ginger, and creamy with coconut milk. This is my pastry-topped tribute to that dish.\n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need a 1.2 litre/2 pint pie dish and a lattice cutter.\n', 90, 90, 6, 20),
(1088, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/porkandwalnutslicesh_93328\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spaghetti_vongle_23082\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spaghetti_vongle_23082_16x9.jpg\n', ' Spaghetti with clams and chilli\n This traditional Italian seafood pasta dish of clams with chilli, garlic and white wine is great for a date night recipe.\n', 90, 30, 4, 14),
(1089, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rack_of_venison_with_a_97913\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chilli_salad_bowls_22404\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chilli_salad_bowls_22404_16x9.jpg\n', ' Chilli salad bowls\n This is one of the gutsiest salads we’ve come up with – packed with beef and flavour. A proper Hairy Dieters’ feast. If you like, you can also make this with ready-made taco shells which are even lower in calories than tortillas so you can eat more filling!This meal provides 397 kcal per portion.\n', 30, 90, 4, 23),
(1090, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/marmalade_pudding_48579\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_jhal_faraizi_karhai_92693\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chunky_cheese_loaf_74948\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02828qx.jpg\n Chunky cheese loaf \n Sweet apple and salty cheese make a scrumptious tea bread that is great to make with kids - only a little grown-up help required.\n', 30, 30, 5, 9),
(1091, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cheats_salted_caramel_71714\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cheats_salted_caramel_71714_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cheat\'s salted caramel sauce\n', ' This is so easy - don\'t tell anyone. A jar of salted caramel makes a great Christmas present. If you don’t want the rum, just leave it out. It still tastes amazing.\n You will need to have sterilised jars to keep the caramel in. This recipe makes about 2 jam jars of caramel.\n', 30, 10, 2, 4),
(1092, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roast_crispy_pork_belly_75553\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roast_crispy_pork_belly_75553_16x9.jpg\n', 'Crispy roast pork belly with egg fried rice\n', ' Ken Hom’s classic crispy pork takes time to prepare but demands no great skill. Egg fried rice is a great way to use up leftover rice.\n', 480, 120, 4, 14),
(1093, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/focaccia_82368\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07f3qv9.jpg\n', 'Focaccia\n', ' Make rosemary-topped focaccia the traditional way, kneading and knocking back the dough by hand.\n', 120, 90, 8, 9),
(1094, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/deep-fried_pork_chops_75525\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salad_cream_31658\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/asparagus_and_goats_curd_57758\n', ' https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/simple_chorizo_and_bean_62033\n https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/simple_chorizo_and_bean_62033_16x9.jpg\n Simple chorizo and bean stew\n Spice up your stew with chorizo and stir in some cannellini beans for a super dinner on a budget. \n Each serving provides 517 kcal, 30g protein, 45g carbohydrates (of which 13g sugars), 21g fat (of which 7g saturates), 17g fibre and 2g salt.\n \n Find out how you could cut your food bills with the Eat Well for Less quiz. \n \n', 30, 30, 2, 10),
(1095, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/herbed_leg_of_lamb_63592\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/herbed_leg_of_lamb_63592_16x9.jpg\n', 'Herbed leg of lamb \n', ' Recipes come into being in strange ways. The fabulous Brazilian pit master and chef, André Lima de Luca, told me about a way he had for slow-cooking a shoulder of pork with (among many other ingredients) oregano, rosemary, orange and lemon. The thought and flavours percolated at the back of my mind for a while – and then I tried cooking a leg of lamb with them last Easter. \n', 90, 120, 6, 9),
(1096, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/veggie_dippers_with_49319\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/veggie_dippers_with_49319_16x9.jpg\n', 'Veggie dippers with chilli dip and aioli\n', ' These veggie dippers from Eat Well for Less are a tasty way to get extra veg into the family. You can use broccoli florets or green beans if you prefer.\n For this recipe you will need a food processor.\n', 30, 30, 4, 19),
(1097, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lamb_with_hummus_and_07348\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lamb_with_hummus_and_07348_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lamb with hummus and tortillas\n', ' Homemade hummus is easy to make and tastes great. It is perfect for wraps and can be kept in the fridge for up to three days.\n For this recipe you will need a blender or food processor to make the hummus.\n \n This meal is low calorie and provides 523 kcal, 37.6g protein, 52.2g carbohydrate (of which 8.2g sugars), 17.1g fat (of which 7.6g saturates), 10.5g fibre and 1.6g salt per portion.\n', 90, 30, 4, 12),
(1098, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/gypsy_tart_81908\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027w0my.jpg\n', 'Gypsy tart\n', ' Muscovado sugar lends a rich caramel flavour to this unique, very sweet tart. Serve with a little crème fraîche or plain yoghurt to balance the sweetness.\n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need a 20cm/8in loose-based tart tin (about 4.5cm/1¾in deep).\n', 30, 90, 6, 8),
(1099, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/duck_burger_and_chips_40267\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/duck_burger_and_chips_40267_16x9.jpg\n', 'Duck burger and chips\n', ' This is a burger like no other: a melting scoop of Vacherin cheese encased in minced duck meat and served in a brioche bun with girolle mushrooms. Delish.\n Equipment and preparation: You will need a mincer for this recipe (alternatively, ask your butcher to mince the duck meat).\n', 30, 30, 2, 10),
(1100, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spatchcocked_duck_with_72827\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282c64.jpg\n', 'Spatchcocked duck with posh peas and celeriac chips\n', ' This is a great treat. Spatchcocking ensures the meat cooks evenly and you get loads of crispy skin.\n', 30, 120, 4, 14),
(1101, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_cooker_pulled_pork_91351\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow_cooker_pulled_pork_91351_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker pulled pork buns\n', ' Pulled pork made in a slow cooker has to be one of the easiest recipes ever! Bung it all in, sit back and in a few hours’ time you’ll be tucking into tender, rich, delicious pork. \n', 30, 120, 4, 10),
(1102, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/grilled_pork_chops_with_74983\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/katys_carrot_and_squash_66459\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/breadandbutterpuddin_88983\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/breadandbutterpuddin_88983_16x9.jpg\n Classic bread and butter pudding\n Beautiful crisp edges and a soft custardy middle - this is what every girl (especially Nigella) looks for in a bread and butter pudding.\n', 30, 90, 8, 11),
(1103, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/best_vegetable_lasagne_50381\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/best_vegetable_lasagne_50381_16x9.jpg\n', 'Veggie lasagne \n', ' Sweet potato, peppers, courgette and spinach combine to make this easy veggie lasagne. We really do think this is the best vegetable lasagne recipe we\'ve ever tried.\n Each serving provides 602 kcal, 21g protein, 60g carbohydrate (of which 19g sugars), 29g fat (of which 15g saturates), 7g fibre and 1.3g salt.\n', 30, 120, 6, 23),
(1104, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/dried_fruit_compote_with_78675\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/whiteirishstew_80062\n', 'None\n', ' White Irish stew\n The essence of Irish stew is to use readily available seasonal ingredients. Traditionally it was a white stew of lamb, potatoes and very little else. This is our take on it. Use the best ingredients you can find - it will be worth it.\n', 30, 120, 4, 11),
(1105, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mixed_bean_salad_89055\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mixed_bean_salad_89055_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mixed bean salad\n', ' Grab that tin of beans from the back of your store cupboard and whip up this simple salad. \n Each serving provides 107kcal, 3g protein, 8g carbohydrate (of which	2g sugars), 6g fat (of which 1g saturates),	4g fibre and 0.1g salt.\n', 30, 0, 6, 13),
(1106, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/oxtail_soup_with_mini_37306\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p017j575.jpg\n', 'Oxtail soup with mini parsley dumplings\n', ' A really warming traditional winter soup with added dumplings, so there’s no need for bread.\n', 30, 120, 6, 20),
(1107, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mixed_seafood_in_a_40876\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vflf.jpg\n', 'Mixed seafood in a Bengali broth (Macher jhol)\n', ' Spice up your seafood with this flavourful Bengali fish stew. \n', 30, 90, 4, 32),
(1108, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicedfriedokra_86577\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastedtomatoandthym_93625\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastedtomatoandthym_93625_16x9.jpg\n', ' Roasted tomato soup with double-baked cheese potatoes\n These crispy cheesy baked potatoes make a bowl of tomato soup seem special. Pick the sweetest ripe tomatoes for best results.\n', 90, 120, 4, 17),
(1109, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/glamming_up_a_cheese_95592\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02srh40.jpg\n', 'Glamming up a cheese board\n', ' Make your cheese board extra special with James Martin\'s indulgent recipe. \n', 30, 30, 6, 31),
(1110, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/grilled_mackerel_with_85479\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/blinis_3759\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/blinis_3759_16x9.jpg\n', ' Blinis\n Make up a batch of these blinis for a party – if the recipe gives you too many you can freeze them. Delicious served with smoked salmon and soured cream, or maybe a spot of caviar.\n', 90, 10, 32, 6),
(1111, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/baked_crab_poblano_with_42581\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smokedduckandpotatos_84673\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', ' Smoked duck and sesame potato salad\n None\n', 30, 90, 4, 15),
(1112, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/wilted_red_cabbage_with_74108\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/wilted_red_cabbage_with_74108_16x9.jpg\n', 'Wilted red cabbage with ham hock\n', ' An easy way to turn leftover ham into a healthy meal. Homemade mayonnaise on red cabbage with no cooking needed.\n', 90, 0, 4, 8),
(1113, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fruit_tarts_77282\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fruit_tarts_77282_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fruit tarts\n', ' Serve these fruit tarts alongside a selection of other cakes and sandwiches cut into triangles for a delicious afternoon tea. \n Equipment: You will need 10cm/4in tartlet cases or barquette tins.\n', 90, 30, 18, 13),
(1114, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/figandchocolatetarts_84848\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02828qx.jpg\n', 'Dark chocolate and fresh fig tarts\n', ' Fresh figs and dark chocolate make a wonderfully rich and succulent dessert. Served with raspberry sauce and white chocolate ice-cream.\n', 90, 90, 4, 16),
(1115, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lambpepperandpineapp_91704\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lambpepperandpineapp_91704_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lamb, pepper and pineapple kebabs with lime, chilli and coriander mayonnaise\n', ' Try a pineapple marinade on cheaper cuts of meat - and let the enzymes work their magic for sweet, tender barbecue food with a Jamaican feel.\n', 120, 30, 10, 22),
(1116, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/canadianbuttermilkpa_70009\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/canadianbuttermilkpa_70009_16x9.jpg\n', 'Buttermilk pancakes\n', ' These are the buttermilk pancakes that a certain Madame Lafond made for me when I was in Quebec; delightfully easy but tasting so light and fluffy.\n', 30, 30, 6, 8),
(1117, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pizzoccheri_88971\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Pizzoccheri\n', ' None\n', 30, 30, 4, 12),
(1118, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bangerswithgreenmash_2962\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bangerswithgreenmash_2962_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bangers with herby mash and onion gravy\n', ' Sausage and mash is the ultimate comfort food – try our recipe complete with a quick onion gravy.\n', 30, 90, 4, 13),
(1119, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mini_victoria_sponge_61310\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mini_victoria_sponge_61310_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mini Victoria sponge cakes\n', ' We’ve zapped the classic Mary Berry Victoria sponge with a shrink ray to make these adorable little cakes.\n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need a 12-cup mini sandwich tin and a piping bag fitted with a 1cm/½in plain nozzle\n', 30, 30, 12, 9),
(1120, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tomatomozzarellaandb_87868\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tomatomozzarellaandb_87868_16x9.jpg\n', 'Homemade pizza\n', ' Make your own homemade pizza with your choice of toppings. Simon Rimmer shows you how to make pizza bases at home for a delicious and easy dinner.\n', 90, 30, 4, 10);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(1121, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/warm_winter_salad_01455\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/warm_winter_salad_01455_16x9.jpg\n', 'Warm salad of pancetta, sweet potato and Brussels sprouts\n', ' A warm and indulgent festive salad that works well as a starter or buffet dish.\n', 30, 90, 4, 24),
(1122, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pumpkinpie_70659\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pumpkinpie_70659_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pumpkin pie\n', ' How to make homemade pumpkin pie in eight simple steps - no need to be spooked! Choose dense, sweet pumpkins rather than using a large watery jack-o\'lantern.\n', 30, 90, 8, 10),
(1123, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/party_vol-au-vents_60239\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07f3sp4.jpg\n', 'Party vol-au-vents\n', ' Combine a basic white sauce and shop-bought puff pastry with a few tasty ingredients to create this party classic.\n', 90, 30, 30, 14),
(1124, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/braised_hogget_pie_16464\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p03dqdjb.jpg\n', 'Braised hogget pie\n', ' This hearty lamb hotpot topped with sliced potatoes is a delicious dish to share with family or friends.\n', 30, 120, 6, 14),
(1125, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/braised_chicken_turbigo_17260\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02sr8pt.jpg\n', 'Braised chicken turbigo\n', ' Traditionally made with kidneys, turbigo is a rich, stew-like dish. Brian uses chicken in this version, which works perfectly with the richness of the black pudding.  \n', 30, 120, 4, 14),
(1126, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mangopassionwithhone_67097\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mangopassionwithhone_67097_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mango passion with honey and yoghurt\n', ' This quick and easy dessert is a light way to finish off a South-east Asian meal.\n Each serving provides 234kcal,	7g protein, 26g carbohydrate (of which 26g sugars), 10g fat (of which 7g saturates), 4g fibre and 0.2g salt.\n', 120, 0, 2, 5),
(1127, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/halloween_ghost_cupcakes_04170\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/halloween_ghost_cupcakes_04170_16x9.jpg\n', 'Halloween ghost cupcakes\n', ' Halloween food doesn\'t have to be gory. These cute ghost cupcakes are great for younger kids\' Halloween parties.\n', 90, 90, 18, 13),
(1128, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/seabreamcookedwithch_70347\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Sea bream cooked with cherry tomatoes\n', ' A simple fish dish that tastes like summer. \n', 30, 30, 4, 9),
(1129, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/macaroni_cheese_51582\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/macaroni_cheese_51582_16x9.jpg\n', 'Macaroni cheese with leeks\n', ' This easy four-step recipe for macaroni cheese will please all the family.  Get a little extra vegetables into your mac and cheese with sweet leeks tucked in the cheese sauce and peas alongside.\n', 30, 90, 4, 12),
(1130, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/neckoflambwithlemona_8863\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/neckoflambwithlemona_8863_16x9.jpg\n', 'Neck of lamb with lemon and thyme\n', ' Neck of lamb is a cheaper cut of meat, but no less delicious if cooked long and slow with plenty of seasoning.\n', 30, 90, 5, 13),
(1131, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salt_fish_fritters_01411\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/salt_fish_fritters_01411_16x9.jpg\n', 'Salt fish fritters\n', ' These West Indian salt fish fritters are perfect finger food. Serve with plenty of pepper sauce for dipping.\n', 480, 30, 24, 7),
(1132, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/asparagus_with_pearl_43154\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/asparagus_with_pearl_43154_16x9.jpg\n', 'Asparagus with pearl barley and bacon\n', ' Hearty and nutritious barley is given a makeover in this creamy springtime supper.\n', 30, 90, 4, 14),
(1133, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/theultimatechocolate_73731\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p076mwwq.jpg\n', 'Chocolate orange roulade\n', ' Mary Berry fills her simple chocolate roulade with orange flavoured cream and tops it with slices of orange that have been soaked in orange liqueur.  \n For this recipe you will need a 33x23cm/13x9in Swiss roll tin.\n', 480, 30, 6, 8),
(1134, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smoothie_oat_bowl_88912\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smoothie_oat_bowl_88912_16x9.jpg\n', 'Smoothie bowl\n', ' Oats are a great way to start the day. Here they are blitzed with fruit and coconut water to make a delicious slow-release vegan smoothie. Topped with more fruit and some chia seeds, this is a really substantial smoothie bowl to keep you full until lunchtime. \n Each serving provides 200 kcal, 3g protein, 33g carbohydrate (of which 25g sugars), 5g fat (of which 2g saturates), 8g fibre and 0.1g salt.\n', 30, 0, 2, 7),
(1135, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/potato_risotto_with_51961\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Potato risotto with braised North Sea squid\n', ' An unusual twist on classic risotto combined with braised squid makes this a dish you won\'t forget quickly. \n', 30, 120, 2, 25),
(1136, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/turkey_meatballs_26601\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/turkey_meatballs_26601_16x9.jpg\n', 'Turkey meatballs\n', ' Try this healthier twist on a classic family recipe. Turkey is traditionally leaner than chicken and using mince made with thigh meat helps to keep these meatballs really moist.\n', 90, 90, 4, 19),
(1137, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_and_rosewater_70042\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_and_rosewater_70042_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken and rosewater biryani\n', ' The rice in a biryani should be so dry and fluffy that when you throw a handful on the floor, all the grains should separate. The secret is to parboil the rice so that the surface is soft and cooked but the centre is still hard, and also to make sure that the main ingredient, i.e. the chicken, mutton, seafood or vegetables, is intensely flavoured but not surrounded by too much ‘gravy’, which will make the rice soggy when the final cooking in a sealed pot takes place. \n', 120, 120, 6, 23),
