(1503, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tournedos_of_venison_87389\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/moroccan_goat_tagine_09469\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rich_moist_all-purpose_35561\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/rich_moist_all-purpose_35561_16x9.jpg\n Rich all-purpose fruit cake\n Dan Lepard\'s cake is very easy to make with a moist crumb and no need to soak the fruit – it\'s ideal for wedding cakes or christening cakes.\n', 30, 120, 25, 19),
