(1606, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tarte_flambe_95147\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tarte_flambe_95147_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tarte flambée \n', ' I was first introduced to tarte flambée with the explanation that it’s France\'s answer to pizza. In fact, it’s not much like pizza at all, apart from being very thin and savoury. As it is made with unleavened dough, it bakes very crisply indeed, which is its great quality. I know you can get tarte flambée in London, but why it isn’t as famous as pizza escapes me. \n', 30, 30, 4, 9),
(1607, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/strawberry_pavlova_with_02235\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07f40qt.jpg\n', 'Strawberry pavlova with vanilla cream \n', ' This isn’t just any strawberry pavlova, this one is topped with a sticky strawberry glaze and drizzled with caramel for a fancy finish.\n', 30, 120, 6, 10),
(1608, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rosemary_lamb_steaks_43151\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_and_mustard_hot_64001\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_and_mustard_hot_64001_16x9.jpg\n', ' Chicken and mustard hot pot \n This hotpot from Eat Well for Less? is an easy way to use up roast chicken leftovers, including gravy, vegetables and roast potatoes. \n Watch the video for three ways to use up leftover roast chicken. Get the Chinese chicken and sweetcorn noodle soup recipe here or find the spiced chicken fajitas recipe here.\n', 30, 30, 2, 8),
(1609, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/berry_ice_cream_03943\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/berry_ice_cream_03943_16x9.jpg\n', 'No-churn berry ice cream \n', ' Easy homemade ice cream is a real treat. You don’t need an ice cream maker for this recipe, you only need a bowl, a whisk and a tub to freeze it in. \n', 120, 0, 10, 5),
(1610, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/blackcurrantmeringue_87044\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027v774.jpg\n', 'Blackcurrant meringue\n', ' None\n', 30, 10, 1, 6),
(1611, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/make-ahead_christmas_33532\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/make-ahead_christmas_33532_16x9.jpg\n', 'Make-ahead Christmas gravy\n', ' Reduce stress on Christmas day by making your gravy in advance. \n', 30, 120, 6, 9),
(1612, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/applepie_89624\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02828qx.jpg\n', 'Apple pie\n', ' Deep-filled apple pie, with rich buttery pastry, orange juice soaked raisins plus a few top tips to make your pie perfect.\n', 90, 30, 4, 13),
(1613, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/grilledredmulletwith_83924\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p028277n.jpg\n', 'Grilled red mullet with squid, flatleaf parsley and capers\n', ' None\n', 30, 30, 4, 18),
(1614, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roast_chicken_with_13305\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roast_chicken_with_13305_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken traybake with chorizo, tomato and red peppers\n', ' This lovely roast chicken traybake is so generous that you’d be hard-pressed to notice it’s low-cal. The chorizo flavours the dish beautifully – a properly filling week-night dinner. \n Each serving provides 505 kcal, 47g protein, 27g carbohydrates (of which 15g sugars), 21g fat (of which 5.5g saturates), 11g fibre and 1g salt. \n', 30, 90, 4, 12),
(1615, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cappucino_pavlova_09523\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cappucino_pavlova_09523_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cappuccino pavlova\n', ' I have long been a pavaholic but this is my first venture into a fruit-free version. The instant espresso powder (do not use regular instant coffee granules) gives bitter oomph to the sweet, marshmallowy meringue.\n', 30, 120, 1, 8),
(1616, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/malaysianspicednoodl_88721\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/malaysianspicednoodl_88721_16x9.jpg\n', 'Malaysian-spiced noodles with tofu\n', ' Aromatic, rich and spicy – proof, if you ever needed it, that vegan food is anything but bland. This vegan noodle soup with crispy tofu is full of flavour.\n This meal provides 712 kcal, 18g protein, 81g carbohydrate (of which 4g sugars), 34g fat (of which 17g saturates), 1g fibre and 3g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 4, 19),
(1617, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/poached_egg_with_toasted_26578\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p017thg3.jpg\n', 'Poached egg with toasted brioche and hazelnut-crumbed asparagus\n', ' Take poached egg and asparagus to another level with this fancy breakfast dish of poached egg with asparagus rubbed in hazelnuts, brioche crumbs and a drizzle of maple syrup.\n', 30, 30, 4, 7),
(1618, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spanish_tomato_bread_15677\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spanish_tomato_bread_15677_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spanish tomato bread\n', ' A classic catalan dish that’s very simple and easy to prepare but totally more-ish. Add to a tapas selection. \n This bread, if served as 8 slices, provides 209kcal, 7g protein, 34g carbohydrate (of which 2g sugars), 4.5g fat (of which 0.5g saturates), 2g fibre and 1g salt per portion.\n', 30, 0, 6, 5),
(1619, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/feta_filo_triangles_37808\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/feta_filo_triangles_37808_16x9.jpg\n', 'Feta and greens filo triangles\n', ' Serve these filo triangles straight out of the oven with the sweet chilli sauce, or they make a great next-day work lunch or part of a picnic spread.\n Each serving provides 360 kcal, 16g protein, 35g carbohydrates (of which 13g sugars), 17g fat (of which 5g saturates), 4g fibre and 1.5g salt.\n \n', 30, 120, 6, 19),
(1620, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rhubarb_and_custard_56928\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/rhubarb_and_custard_56928_16x9.jpg\n', 'Rhubarb and custard\n', ' This dessert is a celebration of a quintessentially British fruit. What excites the tastebuds as much as different flavours is contrasting textures, so in this dessert we have tart rhubarb jelly studded with tender fruit; sweet, smooth, velvety custard; and a garnish of crisp dried rhubarb.\n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need a sugar thermometer, a hand-held blender, 4 glass serving dishes and a silicone mat.\n \n \n', 120, 120, 4, 16),
(1621, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sage_onion_and_sausage_33868\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sage_onion_and_sausage_33868_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sage, onion and sausage stuffing balls\n', ' Stuffing makes for a glorious Christmas side dish, this recipe can be made in advance to reduce stress on the big day. \n Want to make this recipe gluten-free or vegetarian? Check the tips section. \n', 90, 90, 8, 7),
(1622, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/soft_chocolate_cookies_68397\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/warmbaconandchickenl_85044\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p028263m.jpg\n', ' Warm bacon and chicken liver salad\n None\n', 30, 30, 1, 13),
(1623, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tomato_chickpea_and_78792\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tomato_chickpea_and_78792_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tomato, chickpea and pasta soup\n', ' This cheap, quick and easy soup is based on an Italian classic: Pasta e ceci. If you’ve got any fresh herbs to hand, sprinkle a small handful over each bowl of soup before serving. Flatleaf parsley, basil and sage would all work well. \n Each serving provides 391 kcal, 14g protein, 44g carbohydrate (of which 8g sugars), 15g fat (of which 2g saturates), 10g fibre and 0.1g salt.\n \n', 30, 30, 2, 8);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(1624, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lamb_shawarma_with_06754\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lamb_shawarma_with_06754_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lamb shawarma with couscous and raita \n', ' This slow roast lamb shawarma makes a simple and relaxed Sunday lunch. The lamb joint is large enough to serve eight, so double the couscous and raita recipe if you\'re looking for an easy way to feed a crowd.\n Each serving provides 994 kcal, 88g protein, 74g carbohydrate (of which 14g sugars), 35g fat (of which 12g saturates), 15g fibre and 1.7g salt.\n', 30, 120, 4, 27),
(1625, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salmon_and_scallop_95435\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_and_mushroom_pie_15924\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027w5yg.jpg\n', ' Beef, kidney and mushroom pie with a homemade puff pastry lid\n A traditional pie made extra special by the addition of homemade puff pastry. Making your own puff pastry is tricky, but stick with it and you will be rewarded with buttery flaky gorgeousness. \n', 120, 120, 6, 22),
(1626, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fiery_octopus_ojingeo_90139\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p01tlnx0.jpg\n', 'Fiery octopus (Ojingeo bokkeum)\n', ' Korean red chilli paste and red chilli powder add an unusual dimension to this spicy octopus dish. Source them online or from an Asian supermarket.\n', 30, 10, 2, 15),
(1627, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/dundee_cake_22157\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/dundee_cake_22157_16x9.jpg\n', 'Dundee cake\n', ' This delicious afternoon cake is best served with a hunk of cheese and a hot cup of tea.\n', 30, 120, 10, 14),
(1628, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicy_chicken_with_69769\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spicy_chicken_with_69769_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spicy chicken with vegetable ragù\n', ' Spice up chicken breasts or thighs with this simple, low-fat spicy marinade that can prepared the day before.\n Each serving provides 618kcal, 79g protein, 23g carbohydrate (of which 21g sugars), 21g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 10g fibre and 0.5g salt.\n', 120, 90, 2, 19),
(1629, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rye_bread_87040\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/rye_bread_87040_16x9.jpg\n', 'Paul Hollywood\'s rye bread\n', ' Black treacle adds a rich sweetness to this rye loaf. Perfect for posh picnic sandwiches.\n Equipment and preparation: You will need a large, round proving basket for this recipe.\n', 480, 90, 1, 6),
(1630, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/crunchy_banana_yoghurt_48211\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/crunchy_banana_yoghurt_48211_16x9.jpg\n', 'Crunchy banana yoghurt\n', ' Banana and yoghurt are a perfect low-calorie breakfast combination that will keep you going until lunchtime. The banana adds sweetness without the need for extra sugar and the seeds bring a satisfying crunch.\n As part of an Intermittent diet plan, 1 serving provides:\n Your daily piece of fruit\n 2 of your 3 daily low-fat dairy portions\n \n This meal provides 149 kcal per portion.\n \n \n', 30, 0, 2, 4),
(1631, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/moroccanlambtaginewi_84062\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/moroccanlambtaginewi_84062_16x9.jpg\n', 'Moroccan lamb tagine with lemon and pomegranate couscous\n', ' This aromatic lamb tagine can be made in advance and reheated. Make the fruity lemon couscous just before serving.\n', 30, 120, 12, 21),
(1632, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/how_to_make_an_omelette_22250\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/how_to_make_an_omelette_22250_16x9.jpg\n', 'How to make an omelette\n', ' Dill and lemon zest give this simple omelette an edge of fresh springtime flavour. You could easily replace the asparagus, courgettes and goats\' cheese to make your own variations.\n Each serving provides 351kcal, 26g protein, 4g carbohydrate (of which 4g sugars), 25g fat (of which 9g saturates), 2.5g fibre and 0.9g salt.\n', 30, 30, 4, 12),
(1633, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/silk_handkerchief_pasta_32040\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/silk_handkerchief_pasta_32040_16x9.jpg\n', 'Silk handkerchief pasta with pesto\n', ' A pasta and pesto dish from Liguria, home of the best basil in Italy, giving us the famous pesto al Genovese.\n', 90, 10, 4, 11),
(1634, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cranberry_sage_stuffing_52811\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_fricasse_02463\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_fricasse_02463_16x9.jpg\n', ' Chicken fricassée \n Use a whole jointed chicken to give maximum flavour in this comforting classic chicken fricassée recipe. Best served on creamy mash.\n', 30, 30, 4, 17),
(1635, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/arbroath_smokie_cakes_32036\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/arbroath_smokie_cakes_32036_16x9.jpg\n', 'Arbroath-smokie fish cakes with chilli jam\n', ' Arbroath smokies are a special type of smoked haddock and well worth tracking down for these delicious fish cakes.\n', 30, 30, 4, 25),
(1636, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_chickpea_red_30555\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spiced_chickpea_red_30555_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spiced chickpea, red pepper, aubergine and quinoa grain bowl\n', ' Smoky griddled aubergine with subtly spiced chickpeas and cooling yoghurt will make your lunch the envy of the office. \n', 30, 30, 1, 9),
(1637, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/americanchocolaterip_6334\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/americanchocolaterip_6334_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate ripple cheesecake\n', ' Mary Berry adds a swirl of cocoa to this baked chocolate cheesecake for an incredible dessert.\n', 30, 90, 8, 7),
(1638, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_and_peppermint_25149\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_and_peppermint_25149_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate and peppermint roulade\n', ' This roulade was inspired by the nostalgic flavour of after-dinner mints. Bitter dark chocolate and a cool peppermint fondant centre.\n', 30, 90, 8, 9),
(1639, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/three-tier_red_velvet_17795\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/three-tier_red_velvet_17795_16x9.jpg\n', 'Three-tier red velvet cake \n', ' We show you how to make a wedding cake or celebration cake with our simple but impressive recipe.\n Equipment and preparation: For this recipe you will need a 15cm/6in, 23cm/9in and 30cm/12in round cake tin and cake board. You will also need eight dowelling rods (available from specialist cake shops)\n \n', 30, 120, 100, 13),
(1640, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/egg_bacon_and_asparagus_32159\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/egg_bacon_and_asparagus_32159_16x9.jpg\n', 'Egg, bacon and asparagus flan\n', ' A light tart that melts in the mouth, this feels like a real treat and it’s a cinch to make. There’s not even any rolling involved. If you like, leave asparagus out of the filling mixture or add extra ingredients of your own. Sautéed mushrooms, blanched broccoli and roasted peppers all work well. 245 calories per portion\n', 90, 90, 6, 12),
(1641, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/goat_biryani_55073\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/goat_biryani_55073_16x9.jpg\n', 'Goat biryani\n', ' A biryani is perfect for a celebration. This one is topped with a fried duck egg and decorated with coriander. If you can\'t find goat, use cubed leg of lamb instead.\n', 90, 120, 8, 28),
(1642, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/steamed_lobster_27858\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mincemeat_brownies_with_27556\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/panfriedfilletofseab_89000\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02829nh.jpg\n Pan-fried fillet of sea bass, sautéed Baby Gem lettuce with prawn and chorizo \'cassoulet\'\n None\n', 480, 90, 2, 23),
(1643, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_sukiyaki_84557\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p01t7nnh.jpg\n', 'Beef sukiyaki \n', ' Kobe beef is said to be the best quality wagyu (‘Japanese cow’) in the world. But if you can’t source kobe, any good-quality beef will do the trick for this delicious Japanese stew.\n', 30, 30, 4, 18),
(1644, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pork_beans_and_kimchi_91059\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickenliverpate_85880\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chickenliverpate_85880_16x9.jpg\n', ' Chicken liver pâté\n This is the perfect Christmas day starter using chicken livers, a wonderful low cost yet luxury ingredient. \n', 30, 30, 4, 15),
(1645, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sardine_beccafico_51534\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sardine_beccafico_51534_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sardine beccafico\n', ' Enjoy Mediterranean flavours with this summery starter of stuffed baked sardines – ready to eat in just 20 minutes.\n', 30, 10, 6, 14),
(1646, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/savoury_pancakes_with_52388\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/savoury_pancakes_with_52388_16x9.jpg\n', 'Savoury pancakes with ham and cheese\n', ' Why stick to lemon and sugar pancakes when this savoury pancake recipe can kick off a night of batter-based feasting? Flippin\' marvellous.\n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(1647, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lamb_tagine_96490\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/gemelli_with_anchovies_80715\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/gemelli_with_anchovies_80715_16x9.jpg\n', ' Gemelli with anchovies, tomatoes and mascarpone\n Quick, simple and – much as I hate the word – tasty. I know no self-respecting Italian would let tomato seeds sully a sauce, but I do so very happily, and it’s the gloop inside the halved cherry tomatoes that adds cohesion to the spicy, tangy creaminess. \n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(1648, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/black_forest_cranachan_06130\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/black_forest_cranachan_06130_16x9.jpg\n', 'Black Forest cranachan\n', ' This boozy, decadent cranachan combines chocolate, cherries and lashings of cream to create an easy, modern-day trifle.\n', 30, 30, 4, 8),
(1649, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roast_chicken_with_54406\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/herbycouscouswithbut_92552\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/herbycouscouswithbut_92552_16x9.jpg\n', ' Butternut squash tagine with couscous\n Sweet butternut squash with sour preserved lemons makes a fragrant and easy vegetarian tagine with herby couscous on the side.\n', 30, 30, 4, 21),
(1650, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tuna_rocket_and_lemon_95118\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tuna_rocket_and_lemon_95118_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pasta with tuna and rocket\n', ' This tuna pasta recipe is just as good cold as it is hot, so use any leftovers to make packed lunches. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n', 30, 30, 4, 9),
(1651, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_and_ale_stew_with_57183\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beef_and_ale_stew_with_57183_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beef and ale stew with horseradish dumplings\n', ' Got a crowd to feed? Mary\'s hearty beef and ale stew recipe is perfect and the oven does most of the work for you. \n For this recipe you will need a deep ovenproof casserole dish with a lid.\n', 90, 120, 6, 19),
(1652, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mocha_swirls_42049\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mocha_swirls_42049_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mocha swirls \n', ' Very like cinnamon buns, but without the cinnamon, Nadiya\'s mocha swirls are laced with coffee and chocolate, rolled up and topped with a sticky sweet espresso icing. \n', 30, 30, 9, 14),
(1653, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/buccatini_with_sardines_06956\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p075zb20.jpg\n', 'Bucatini with sardines and anchovies (pasta con le sarde)\n', ' This classic Sicilian dish is an easy pasta recipe perfect for hazy summer evenings. \n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(1654, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicory_gratin_84963\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicory_gratin_84963_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicory gratin\n', ' A beloved classic of Belgian cooking; this is a simple, rustic family dish. The Comté cheese can be replaced by any British cheese. And, of course, omit the ham for a vegetarian version.\n', 30, 120, 2, 14),
(1655, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/harira_soup_63128\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/meatloaf_56639\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/meatloaf_56639_16x9.jpg\n', ' Meatloaf\n This is an American classic and is made here with a combination of beef and pork mince.  \n Delicious served with this wedge salad.\n \n', 30, 120, 8, 22),
(1656, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cider_and_5-spice_bundt_05085\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cider_and_5-spice_bundt_05085_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cider and five-spice bundt cake\n', ' Most of the time I refer to this as my Cider and five-spice gingerbread, but I changed the name out of concern for those who expect a little more gingeriness from their gingerbead. If you want to intensify the ginger element, use 250ml/9fl oz ginger beer in place of the cider.\n This cake is wonderful enough plain as it is, though I have something of a faiblesse for the gleaming accompaniment of the smoky salted caramel sauce, as you can see from the picture.\n \n For this recipe you will need a 2½/4½ pints litre capacity bundt tin or a 20cm/8in square cake tin (approx. 5½cm/2¼in deep).\n', 30, 90, 1, 18),
