(1969, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pizza_expressed_three_77124\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pizza_expressed_three_77124_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pizza expressed three ways\n', ' You can either make the dough from scratch for this pizza, which takes no time at all, or for an even speedier method, buy soft tortillas and use these as a base for the pizza instead of making your own. \n', 30, 10, 3, 26),
(1970, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/baklava_24832\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/baklava_24832_16x9.jpg\n', 'Walnut and honey baklava\n', ' This wonderfully sticky baklava tastes amazing with freshly made mint tea or Turkish coffee, but it\'s generous enough to serve as a dessert. \n', 120, 90, 40, 14),
(1971, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/red-red_stew_with_spiced_28798\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/red-red_stew_with_spiced_28798_16x9.jpg\n', 'Red-red stew with spiced plantain\n', ' Traditionally a red-red stew is made with palm oil and tomatoes. We’ve updated this version of the common Ghanaian dish to use vegetable oil. \n', 30, 120, 4, 27),
(1972, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tandoorichickensamos_93148\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02828qx.jpg\n', 'Tandoori chicken samosas\n', ' Samosas make a great little starter with endless variations on fillings to suit your tastes.\n', 120, 90, 10, 22),
(1973, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushroompancakemamon_83638\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07pc634.jpg\n', 'Mushroom pancake mamon\n', ' A classic French recipe for mushroom crepes. Topped with cream. Obviously.\n', 30, 30, 2, 16),
(1974, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/teriyaki_glazed_salmon_24085\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rosewater_trifle_40749\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02bmps3.jpg\n', ' Rosewater trifle\n A delicately strawberry and rose flavoured dessert, designed to impress. Perfect for a special occasion.\n For this recipe you will need two 20cm/8in cake tins. \n', 30, 120, 6, 17),
(1975, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rioja-braised_lamb_66249\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/rioja-braised_lamb_66249_16x9.jpg\n', 'Rioja-braised lamb shanks with chorizo and garlic\n', ' Once the initial faff of browning the meat is done, this dish requires very little effort and the resulting flavours are intense.\n', 30, 120, 4, 17),
(1976, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sopa_azteca_tortilla_67323\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sopa_azteca_tortilla_67323_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tortilla soup\n', ' This Mexican tortilla soup is often made with pasilla chillies, but I like it with chipotles. I’ve also had this soup with cooked shredded chicken and even crisp pieces of pork skin.\n', 30, 90, 4, 21),
(1977, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rosemary_and_garlic_salt_80067\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spatchcock_chicken_31016\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p076mn4r.jpg\n', ' Lemon and honey spatchcock chicken with quinoa and broad bean salad\n This is the perfect dish for dinning al fresco this summer with its combination exotic flavours of preserved lemon, chillies, green olives and herbs.\n', 480, 30, 4, 21),
(1978, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lasagne_82381\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lasagne_82381_16x9.jpg\n', 'The ultimate lasagne\n', ' The ultimate homemade lasagne, made with beef and pork, fresh pasta, Italian mozzarella and creamy béchamel. Delicious.\n', 90, 120, 10, 22),
(1979, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/hive_cake_03837\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/hive_cake_03837_16x9.jpg\n', 'Hive cake\n', ' This gorgeous lemon and honey flavoured cake with cute smiley bees buzzing round would make a perfect birthday cake.\n', 30, 120, 14, 12),
(1980, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ricotta_beefburger_25500\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/ricotta_beefburger_25500_16x9.jpg\n', 'Ricotta beefburger\n', ' These simple burgers combine creamy ricotta with sharp capers, served with a sun-dried tomato relish.\n', 30, 30, 6, 11),
(1981, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tomato_eggy_bread_36998\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tomato_eggy_bread_36998_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tomato eggy bread\n', ' This tasty spin on a breakfast classic provides energy and protein to get you going in the morning, plus a double dose of tomato.\n Each serving provides 294 kcal, 17g protein, 32g carbohydrates (of which 5g sugars), 10g fat (of which 2g saturates), 6.5g fibre and 1g salt. \n', 30, 10, 2, 10),
(1982, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sausage_rolls_piccalilli_98942\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickenkiev_5492\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027w3zy.jpg\n', ' Parmesan and herb chicken kiev\n None\n', 120, 30, 4, 15),
(1983, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salt_cod_brandade_with_73461\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02826gp.jpg\n', 'Brandade\n', ' This Mediterranean classic makes a perfect warming starter for four people. Plan ahead - the salt cod needs soaking, and the parsley oil needs preparing overnight.\n To make this dish you will need a blender and a food processor. \n', 480, 120, 4, 17),
(1984, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_cooker_minestrone_24914\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow_cooker_minestrone_24914_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker minestrone\n', ' This hearty Italian soup is made with pasta and beans. This minestrone is great for batch cooking, just divide into portions and pop in the freezer and wonderfully warming soup will never be far from your bowl. \n Each serving provides 352kcal, 24g protein, 29g carbohydrate (of which 9.5g sugars), 14g fat (of which 4g saturates), 8.5g fibre and 1.5g salt.\n', 30, 120, 4, 18),
(1985, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastcodwithalemonga_3477\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastcodwithalemonga_3477_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roast cod with a lemon, garlic and parsley crust\n', ' The delicate flavour of cod is wonderfully paired with lemon, garlic and parsley in this simple dish.\n This meal provides 322 kcal, 33g protein, 16g carbohydrate (of which 0.6g sugars), 14g fat (of which 8g saturates), 0.6g fibre and 0.9g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 4, 11),
(1986, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicy_mozzarella_47844\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spicy_mozzarella_47844_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spicy mozzarella aubergines with green beans and chickpeas\n', ' These stuffed aubergines combine wonderfully with the crisp green beans and chickpeas. This is a great stand-alone dish or it could be served with a bowl of couscous.\n Each serving provides 497 kcal, 27g protein, 37g carbohydrates (of which 8.5g sugars), 23g fat (of which 7g saturates), 17g fibre and 3g salt. \n', 30, 90, 2, 11),
(1987, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bunny_chow_17677\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/old_fashioned_rabbit_74225\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/old_fashioned_rabbit_74225_16x9.jpg\n', ' Old fashioned rabbit stew\n Rabbit only needs a few ingredients to be transformed into a delicious one-pot meal.\n', 30, 120, 5, 17),
(1988, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastedchickenbreast_86354\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastedchickenbreast_86354_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roasted chicken breast with leek and green beans\n', ' Angela Hartnett\'s roast chicken breast is serve with a tasty combination of leeks, green beans and fresh herbs. \n', 30, 30, 4, 12),
(1989, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smoked_salmon_00865\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smoked_salmon_00865_16x9.jpg\n', 'Smoked salmon open-topped sandwich \n', ' Using dark rye or wholegrain bread for sandwiches rather than white will increase the fibre content. This high-protein open sandwich with salmon and quark cheese makes a quick and convenient low-calorie lunch. Try topping with cooked and peeled prawns instead of the salmon.\n With a GI of 49 this meal is high protein, low GI and provides 235 kcal per portion.\n', 30, 0, 2, 7),
(1990, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/wobbly_apricot_tart_20144\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/wobbly_apricot_tart_20144_16x9.jpg\n', 'Wobbly apricot tart\n', ' The pastry and marzipan melt over the apricot halves to make a wobbly top for this sweet, and simply delicious, fruit tart.\n', 30, 90, 6, 8),
(1991, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegetablecurry_80763\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegetablecurry_80763_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegetable curry\n', ' An easy veggie curry that makes a cheap and healthy meal. It uses basic storecupboard ingredients so is very quick and easy to cook. It\'s simple to make vegan too, just swap the yoghurt for a dairy-free alternative.\n Each serving provides 335 kcal, 9g protein, 41g carbohydrate (of which 14.5g sugars), 12.5g fat (of which 1.5g saturates), 10g fibre and 0.5g salt.\n', 30, 30, 3, 16),
(1992, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/new_york_chicken_and_67791\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/new_york_chicken_and_67791_16x9.jpg\n', 'New York chicken and apple salad\n', ' A twist on the classic New York-style Waldorf Salad with chicken and a creamy, but low-calorie, garlic dressing. This is a little over 500 calories, so if you are dieting pair it with a lower calorie breakfast or lunch to make sure your intake is no more than 1200–1500 calories.\n Each serving provides 515 kcal, 55.5g protein, 42g carbohydrates (of which 42g sugars), 12.5g fat (of which 2.5g saturates), 5.5g fibre and 0.8g salt. \n \n With a GI of 58 this meal is high protein, low GI.\n', 30, 0, 2, 17),
(1993, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pork_with_red_pepper_and_69190\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pork_with_red_pepper_and_69190_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pork with red pepper and noodles\n', ' This speedy stir-fry can be whipped up in minutes and is packed full of flavour. \n This meal is low calorie and provides 354 kcal, 27g protein, 48g carbohydrate (of which 19g sugars), 5g fat (of which 1.5g saturates), 1g fibre and 2.3g salt.\n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(1994, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/classic_carrot_cake_08513\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/classic_carrot_cake_08513_16x9.jpg\n', 'Classic carrot cake\n', ' Nothing beats a classic carrot cake - this one has a touch of cinnamon and walnuts plus the obligatory cream cheese icing. This cake is a whopper, so make sure you have some hungry bunnies on hand.\n', 30, 120, 1, 12),
(1995, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_avocado_shake_50246\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_avocado_shake_50246_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate avocado shake \n', ' You\'ve heard of chocolate avocado mousse - now try the smoothie with super avocado, banana, honey and cacao. \n Each shake provides 158 kcal, 3g protein, 11g carbohydrate (of which 9g sugars), 11g fat (of which 4.5g saturates), 4g fibre and 0.5g salt. \n', 30, 0, 4, 7),
(1996, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beefstock_1295\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282bb4.jpg\n', 'Beef stock\n', ' None\n', 30, 120, 6, 9),
(1997, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/crispy-skinned_chicken_21035\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_and_cheese_65643\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_and_cheese_65643_16x9.jpg\n', ' Chicken and cheese quesadillas\n Make quesadillas in 10 minutes with this quick and easy Mexican-inspired recipe from The Hairy Bikers.\n', 30, 10, 2, 15),
(1998, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sausagecasserolewith_82366\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sausagecasserolewith_82366_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sausage casserole with beans\n', ' Cook this tasty, spicy, Italian supper, adding more beans if you have extra guests. Save time by using tinned beans. \n', 30, 120, 6, 11),
(1999, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/traditional_wedding_cake_68531\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/traditional_wedding_cake_68531_16x9.jpg\n', 'Traditional wedding cake \n', ' Make your own wedding cake with our step-by-step recipe. The great thing about making a fruit cake is that it can be made well in advance of the big day.\n Equipment and preparation: For this recipe you will need a 15cm/6in, 23cm/9in and 30cm/12in round cake tin, thin cake boards of respective sizes, and 20cm/8in, 28cm/11in and 35cm/14in thick cake boards. You will also need eight dowelling rods and eight cake pillars. All of these are available from specialist cake shops. Plus you will need 5m/16ft 5in x 1.5cm/⅝in pink satin ribbon.\n \n \n', 90, 120, 100, 20);
