(2324, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/buffalomozzarellabru_93627\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/buffalomozzarellabru_93627_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mozzarella bruschetta with shaved fennel and courgette\n', ' To make this rustic nibble daintier, cut rounds from the toast with a cookie cutter and pile a little topping onto each. \n', 30, 10, 1, 11),
(2325, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/christmas_cake_present_81563\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/christmas_cake_present_81563_16x9.jpg\n', 'Christmas cake present\n', ' The perfect Christmas gift? A Christmas cake present! Wrapped up in a traditional double layer of marzipan and fondant, and finished off with gingerbread biscuit tags, this fruit cake makes the perfect present. Fresh holly and mini baubles can also add another decorative festive flourish.\n', 90, 120, 20, 23),
(2326, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/potato_leek_and_cheese_93841\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/potato_leek_and_cheese_93841_16x9.jpg\n', 'Potato, leek and cheese pie\n', ' This is a quick and easy take on flaky pastry. The vegetarian cheese and potato pie filling is also delicious and simple to make. \n', 120, 120, 6, 15),
(2327, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mokatines_96500\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mokatines_96500_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mokatines\n', ' A masterclass in how to turn a simple genoise sponge into something really special. Decorated with chopped nuts and coffee buttercream these individual cakes are packed with flavour.\n For this recipe you will need a shallow 18cm/7in square cake tin and a piping bag fitted with a number 7 star nozzle.\n', 120, 90, 9, 13),
(2328, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/baked_potato_skins_with_28036\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/baked_potato_skins_with_28036_16x9.jpg\n', 'Baked potato with bacon, taleggio and leek\n', ' Taleggio melts wonderfully and makes a delicious topping for baked potato, combined here with bacon and a creamy white wine sauce.\n', 30, 120, 4, 13),
(2329, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_and_apple_tagine_51104\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p017tj7q.jpg\n', 'Beef and apple tagine\n', ' Most slow-cooked Moroccan meat tagines have a sweet note. Here apple, honey and dried prunes add that moreish flavour.\n', 30, 120, 6, 20),
(2330, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pastawithcourgettesa_93036\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pastawithcourgettesa_93036_16x9.jpg\n', 'Courgette pasta with spinach balls\n', ' Make a courgette pasta sauce in this easy vegetarian recipe from Antonio Carluccio. The spinach balls are amazing.\n', 30, 30, 4, 13),
(2331, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/besteverspaghettibol_89567\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p028263m.jpg\n', 'Spaghetti Bolognese with extras\n', ' Simon Rimmer adds all kinds of extras to his Bolognese sauce: peppers, mushrooms and chicken livers. It might just be genius.\n', 30, 90, 4, 17),
(2332, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fishstock_1296\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282bb4.jpg\n', 'Easy fish stock\n', ' This easy fish stock is super easy and quick to make.\n', 30, 30, 1, 8),
(2333, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salmon_in_parma_ham_with_39372\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/salmon_in_parma_ham_with_39372_16x9.jpg\n', 'Salmon in Parma ham with celeriac chips\n', ' Here’s a delicious and easy way to make a good supper with salmon. Celeriac is a great swap for potato, with half the calories.\n Each serving provides 400 kcal, 33g protein, 11g carbohydrates (of which 9g sugars), 22g fat (of which 4g saturates), 14g fibre and 1.1g salt. \n \n With a GI of 45 this meal is high protein, low GI.\n', 30, 90, 4, 13),
(2334, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickenoncrispynoodl_93614\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Chicken on crispy noodles\n', ' A flavourful dish that can be whipped together in no time, perfect for a speedy supper. \n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(2335, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pearl_barley_butternut_61137\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pearl_barley_butternut_61137_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pearl barley, butternut squash and sage risotto\n', ' Pearl barley is much cheaper than traditional risotto rice and more flavoursome too. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n', 30, 90, 4, 9),
(2336, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_almond_caprese_27893\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_almond_caprese_27893_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gluten-free chocolate cake\n', ' This is a rich, decadent, gluten-free chocolate cake from Italy. Serve with authentic, Italian pistachio ice cream for extra delight. \n', 90, 90, 6, 5),
(2337, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/italian_strawberry_and_51490\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/italian_strawberry_and_51490_16x9.jpg\n', 'Italian strawberry and chocolate chunk cake\n', ' A delicious taste of Italy using British strawberries makes for a perfect dessert or afternoon tea. \n You’ll need a 20–22cm cake tin.\n', 30, 120, 8, 14),
(2338, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/miso-baked_black_cod_01223\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p01t6mww.jpg\n', 'Miso-baked black cod \n', ' If you can’t get hold of the deliciously meaty black cod fish, you can use a cheaper fish such as pollock. In the Hairy Bikers Far East programme Si and Dave didn’t have an oven on location, so they fried the fish. It can be either baked or fried.\n', 120, 30, 4, 18),
(2339, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_orange_and_honey_36705\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spiced_orange_and_honey_36705_16x9.jpg\n', 'Snowman pancakes with orange and spice\n', ' Add some festive spice to fluffy pancakes with cinnamon and orange zest. The perfect breakfast for Christmas morning. \n', 30, 30, 6, 8),
(2340, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_and_asparagus_27353\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02ffwz5.jpg\n', 'Chicken and asparagus quiche\n', ' This quick and easy quiche is a tasty way of using up leftover roast chicken - and it makes great picnic food too!\n', 30, 90, 4, 12),
(2341, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/steamedseabassinhotb_89271\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/steamedseabassinhotb_89271_16x9.jpg\n', 'Steamed sea bass in hot beer and ginger lime sauce\n', ' This simple and elegant sea bass recipe makes the most of this delicious fish.\n', 30, 30, 2, 14),
(2342, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_roast_chicken_94425\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spiced_roast_chicken_94425_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spiced roast chicken\n', ' Spice up on your Sunday roast with this Indian-influenced marinade and coconut milk gravy. \n', 90, 120, 4, 27),
(2343, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/adjaruli_khachapuri_76214\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mozzarella_tomato_82203\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mozzarella_tomato_82203_16x9.jpg\n', ' Bruschetta with avocado and olive tapenade \n Mary\'s new favourite lunch – quick and easy to make and oh so tasty. If your ciabatta loaf is long and narrow, cut it on the diagonal to give a larger surface area to hold all the topping.\n For this recipe you need a mini food processor to make the tapenade.\n', 30, 10, 6, 16),
(2344, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/duck_a_lorange_20145\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_supreme_au_vin_16466\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_and_chestnut_69367\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_and_chestnut_69367_16x9.jpg\n Chocolate and chestnut Christmas log\n You\'ll definitely want seconds of this moist, brownie-like cake! The coffee stops it being overly sweet and chestnut purée adds an extra festive touch.\n', 30, 30, 6, 9),
(2345, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smoked_haddock_and_96189\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smoked_haddock_and_96189_16x9.jpg\n', 'Smoked haddock and cauliflower gratin\n', ' Combine the flavours of fish pie and cauliflower cheese and you get this wonderful dish from Mary Berry! A hearty gratin that\'s a real winter wamer.\n', 30, 90, 6, 12),
(2346, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/venison_tartare_hazelnut_86777\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ricotta_and_spinach_03750\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemonchicken_11654\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lemonchicken_11654_16x9.jpg\n Chinese lemon chicken\n This homemade Chinese lemon chicken recipe from James Martin is quick, easy and delicious. No need for a takeaway then! \n', 30, 30, 4, 18),
(2347, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bubble_and_squeak_and_38318\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bubble_and_squeak_and_38318_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bubble and squeak\n', ' This bubble and squeak takes leftover roast or mashed potatoes and any uneaten greens for a simple veggie solution to Christmas leftovers. The candied shallots give it a lovely sweetness.\n', 30, 30, 4, 18),
(2348, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushroomsalad_73189\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Mushroom salad\n', ' None\n', 30, 10, 4, 9),
(2349, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_roasted_lamb_95248\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p010lng1.jpg\n', 'Slow-roasted lamb shoulder and homemade mint sauce\n', ' Lamb shoulder is quite a fatty cut, so wonderful for low, slow roasting. It\'s a foolproof way of feeding a crowd because it nigh on impossible to overcook it.\n', 30, 120, 8, 25),
(2350, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bakedspareribchopswi_89921\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p028277n.jpg\n', 'Baked pork spare rib chops with pears, potatoes, onions and Roquefort butter\n', ' None\n', 120, 90, 4, 17),
(2351, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salted_dark_chocolate_16338\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/salted_dark_chocolate_16338_16x9.jpg\n', 'Salted chocolate cake\n', ' Donna Hay\'s quick and easy chocolate cake has a gorgeous soured cream ganache and a sprinkle of sea salt that lifts the flavour to another level. This will totally impress at any party or bake sale. \n', 30, 90, 10, 11),
(2352, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/griddled_lamb_chops_with_62964\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beetroot_chutney_with_33062\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beetroot_chutney_with_33062_16x9.jpg\n', ' Beetroot chutney\n This lovely fusion of earthy sweet beetroot, zesty lemons and piquant capers, with warming hints of fennel, works well with smoked fish, cold poultry or grilled halloumi. It makes a great barbecue relish for just about anything and is a wonderful partner to cheese. \n', 30, 120, 3, 12),
(2353, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/marys_victoria_sandwich_58140\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/marys_victoria_sandwich_58140_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mary’s Victoria sandwich with buttercream\n', ' For the final technical challenge Mary Berry asked the bakers to make this simple sponge with homemade jam and buttercream – without a recipe. We won\'t be so unkind. Mary\'s perfect Victoria sponge recipe with buttercream is yours.\n For this recipe you will need two 20cm/8in sandwich tins, an electric mixer and piping bag fitted with plain nozzle. \n', 30, 30, 8, 9),
(2354, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/seabasswithroastedre_91745\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Sea bass with roasted red peppers\n', ' None\n', 120, 90, 4, 15),
(2355, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/redpepperandapplemea_88173\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p01tlbt4.jpg\n', 'Red pepper and apple meatballs with sweet and sour sauce\n', ' None\n', 30, 90, 4, 17),
(2356, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/squid_with_oriental_83376\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/carrot_and_ginger_soup_64093\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/carrot_and_ginger_soup_64093_16x9.jpg\n', ' Carrot and ginger soup  \n Quick, easy and mouthwateringly good. This carrot and ginger soup is perfect for chilly afternoons. Why not make a few more portions and keep in the freezer for emergencies?\n Each serving provides 160 kcal, 2g protein, 23g carbohydrate (of which 19g sugars), 4.5g fat (of which 1g saturates), 10g fibre and 0.9g salt.\n', 30, 30, 1, 8),
(2357, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bourbon-glazed_turkey_28426\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_and_wild_04860\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_and_wild_04860_16x9.jpg\n', ' Chicken and wild mushroom pie\n James gives the traditional chicken and mushroom pie a special twist with wonderful wild mushrooms and Madeira. Save on the washing up by baking in the pan used to make the filling or simply bake it in a pie dish. Serve with sautéed greens for a wonderful supper. \n Equipment: you will need an ovenproof frying pan for this recipe.\n', 120, 90, 4, 16),
(2358, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/butternut_soup_with_52337\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p074k0t9.jpg\n', 'Butternut soup with butternut gnocchi\n', ' Step into autumn with butternut gnocchi, all full of amber goodness.\n', 30, 90, 4, 16),
(2359, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_chicken_and_53621\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/focacciawithrosemary_90210\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/focacciawithrosemary_90210_16x9.jpg\n', ' Focaccia with rosemary\n None\n', 120, 90, 2, 8),
(2360, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/taglieriniwithsquida_93785\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027w5ns.jpg\n', 'Taglierini with squid and oven-roasted tomato sauce\n', ' None\n', 480, 120, 4, 14),
(2361, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicy_georgian_beef_soup_47865\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/iced_berries_with_63709\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/iced_berries_with_63709_16x9.jpg\n', ' Iced berries with limoncello white chocolate sauce\n What makes this fantastic for a last-minute, even impromptu, dinner party pud (with interesting Christmas potential) is that you can keep the berries in the deep freeze until needed. I suppose you could, in summer, use fresh berries, though you would lose the contrast between warm rich sauce and sharp icy fruit.\n', 30, 10, 4, 4),
(2362, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/grilledlambwithfetaa_92373\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/grilledlambwithfetaa_92373_16x9.jpg\n', 'Grilled lamb with feta and lemon\n', ' Crisp lamb chops, fresh herbs, lemon and creamy feta are combined in this super-quick supper from Nigel Slater\n', 30, 30, 2, 9),
(2363, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemon_cake_29430\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lemon_cake_29430_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lemon cake\n', ' Easy, but impressive - Raymond Blanc\'s lemon cake recipe has been served at his restaurant for the past 25 years. \n Equipment and preparation: You will need a 26cm x 9cm x 8cm/10in x 3½in x 3in loaf tin.\n', 30, 90, 12, 13),
(2364, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_pecan_tart_86249\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_pecan_tart_86249_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate pecan tart\n', ' Impress the chocoholic in your life with chocolate shortcrust pastry filled with a rich chocolate and nut filling.\n For this recipe you will need a heavy, flat baking tray and a 25cm/10in fluted flan tin.\n', 120, 120, 10, 14),
(2365, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/veggie_bean_burgers_for_53280\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/veggie_bean_burgers_for_53280_16x9.jpg\n', 'Veggie bean burgers\n', ' These healthy veggie burgers are really easy to make and cost much less than shop-bought alternatives.You can make your own versions at home which can be frozen and then oven-cooked from frozen as needed. They can all be served with dips or as a filling for pittas, flatbreads or wraps. It is good to add a vegetable of some kind- mashed squash, carrot or sweet potato work really well- you can mash these from boiled or roasted vegetables.\n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(2366, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vincisgrassi_75129\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quick_beef_massaman_36307\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/quick_beef_massaman_36307_16x9.jpg\n', ' Quick beef massaman curry with coconut rice\n When it’s the middle of the week and you need curry in a hurry, this quick Thai curry is just the thing. \n', 30, 30, 2, 21),
(2367, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chargrilledtunawithr_86657\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282bx4.jpg\n', 'Chargrilled tuna with shoestring fries\n', ' None\n', 30, 90, 4, 13);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(2368, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fennelsausagesbraise_86774\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fennelsausagesbraise_86774_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fennel sausages braised with lemony potatoes and bay leaves\n', ' The perfect sausages for this dish are those from specialist Italian or Continental delicatessens, luganega, which come in one long length. If you are using ordinary sausages, add a teaspoon of fennel seeds to the onions when frying.\n', 30, 90, 4, 14),
(2369, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickpeaandchorizoso_81545\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chickpeaandchorizoso_81545_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken and chorizo stew\n', ' Use tinned chickpeas to make a speedy, spicy, smoky chicken and chorizo stew recipe that will warm you up from head to toe.\n', 480, 120, 6, 14),
(2370, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/americanpancakeswith_86498\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07f404k.jpg\n', 'American-style pancakes with bacon and maple syrup\n', ' Wow - when you really don\'t want to hold back, pile all the toppings on these fluffy American pancakes.\n', 30, 30, 4, 8),
(2371, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chilliapplejelly_7293\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282bb4.jpg\n', 'Chilli apple jelly\n', ' None\n', 120, 120, 1, 4),
(2372, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/springmisosoup_72270\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/springmisosoup_72270_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spring miso soup\n', ' Miso soup is deliciously savoury and comforting. With a good quality stock, this dish takes only a few minutes.\n', 30, 10, 4, 9),
(2373, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/crisp_pork_belly_with_12745\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/thai_pork_kaffir_lime_91692\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cheesesouffl_1326\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p01tlcrc.jpg\n Cheese soufflé\n None\n', 30, 30, 6, 11),
(2374, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/buckwheat_triple_32460\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/buckwheat_triple_32460_16x9.jpg\n', 'Triple chocolate buckwheat cookies\n', ' The star here is the buckwheat, not only because it makes these cookies gluten-free, but mainly because I feel it brings its own nutty flavour and unique texture, creating a cookie that has softness and a shortbready bite, as well as a subtle smokiness. Those who like a truly chewy cookie might find these a little cakey, but I like chewiness in a cookie and yet find constant excuses to make these.\n', 30, 30, 25, 11),
(2375, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/the_colossal_curly_34564\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02bpypx.jpg\n', 'Carrot and orange cake\n', ' Ian made 5 tiers of this cake for the Bake Off final, but here\'s a pared-back version to try at home – it tastes gorgeous!\n', 30, 120, 1, 23),
(2376, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pauls_mincemeat_and_33176\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pauls_mincemeat_and_33176_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mincemeat and marzipan couronne\n', ' This French \'crown\' of bread is chock-full of Christmas ingredients and makes a great alternative to Christmas cake.\n', 120, 30, 12, 14),
(2377, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tapasstylespicytomat_89039\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Tapas-style spicy tomato squid\n', ' None\n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
