(2592, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/braisedredcabbage_81485\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vymn.jpg\n', 'Braised red cabbage with bacon\n', ' Braised red cabbage and bacon work brilliantly together. This easy recipe is a great addition to Christmas dinner. \n', 30, 10, 2, 11),
(2593, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/kale_ricotta_tortelli_10278\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027w5cc.jpg\n', 'Cavolo nero and ricotta tortelli with walnut sauce\n', ' This version of the Italian stuffed pasta dish is made with ricotta and kale, served with a sage-flecked walnut sauce.\n Equipment and preparation: You will need a pasta machine and a serrated pastry wheel.\n \n', 120, 10, 4, 15),
(2594, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/profiteroleswithpist_90242\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/profiteroleswithpist_90242_16x9.jpg\n', 'How to make profiteroles \n', ' Lesley Waters shows you how to make these easy profiteroles. The unfilled, baked profiteroles freeze really well and just need crisping up in a hot oven after defrosting.Equipment and preparation: You will need a plain-nozzle piping bag.\n', 30, 30, 18, 12),
(2595, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/rice_bowl_with_ginger_58307\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/rice_bowl_with_ginger_58307_16x9.jpg\n', 'Rice bowl with ginger, radish and avocado\n', ' A rice bowl is a wondrous thing, but often – despite the simplicity of its title – a rather cluttered and complicated one. Here, I have pared it back, to make a gorgeously seasoned rice bowl, with nothing more than a few seeds, herbs and radishes stirred through it, and an avocado to top it. It’s a simple take on an inspiringly expansive idea. So please use this as a starting point only. It’s very much a non-recipe recipe, and every time I make it, I add something different, depending on what’s to hand.\n', 30, 30, 2, 10),
(2596, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_gingerbread_45369\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spiced_gingerbread_45369_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sticky gingerbread cake\n', ' If you can, wrap and keep this tea time treat for a few days before eating – its stickiness will develop as it matures.\n', 30, 90, 8, 17),
(2597, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smoked_haddock_with_86433\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smoked_haddock_with_86433_16x9.jpg\n', 'Smoked haddock with lentils and spinach \n', ' Smoked haddock is full of flavour, but low in fat and calories, which makes it ideal for a diet.\n Each serving provides 305 kcal, 37g protein, 15.5g carbohydrate (of which 3.5g sugars), 9.5g fat (of which 2g saturates), 5.5g fibre and 1.5g salt.\n', 30, 30, 1, 8),
(2598, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ensaimadas_22045\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pimento_herb_penne_54105\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pimento_herb_penne_54105_16x9.jpg\n', ' Parma ham and pimento penne\n Mary Berry\'s easy pasta combines crispy Parma ham, red peppers and fresh herbs. Parma ham usually comes in packets of six to seven slices – use the whole packet.\n', 30, 30, 4, 11),
(2599, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegetariancottagepie_92035\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegetariancottagepie_92035_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegetarian cottage pie\n', ' A vegetarian take on a classic cottage pie. Beans and veggie mince replace meat, and root vegetables give the mash a unique twist. \n', 30, 90, 4, 22),
(2600, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cullenskink_92467\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cullenskink_92467_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cullen skink\n', ' Cullen skink is a classic Scottish smoked fish soup with velvety leeks and potato. Perfectly warming for winter.\n', 30, 90, 4, 14),
(2601, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fishtacoswithguacamo_90762\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/black_banana_cake_52982\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/black_banana_cake_52982_16x9.jpg\n', ' Black banana cake\n Want to know how to use up overripe bananas? Nigel Slater’s banana bread recipe is just the ticket.\n', 30, 120, 8, 9),
(2602, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roasted_red_pepper_50795\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roasted_red_pepper_50795_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roasted red pepper hummus\n', ' There are no end of varieties of hummus in the supermarket. This one is loaded with sweet roasted red pepper, making it much lighter. \n This meal, if served as eight portions, provides 67kcal, 3g protein, 9g carbohydrate (of which 4g sugars), 1.5g fat (of which 0.2g saturates), 3g fibre and	0.3g salt.\n', 90, 90, 6, 14),
(2603, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/squash_curry_09269\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/squash_curry_09269_16x9.jpg\n', 'Butternut squash and chickpea curry\n', ' An easy vegan butternut squash and chickpea curry that freezes well.\n Each serving provides 493 kcal, 15g protein, 58g carbohydrates (of which 12g sugars), 19g fat (of which 9.5g saturates), 14.5g fibre and 0.5g salt.\n', 30, 90, 6, 19),
(2604, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolatetartwithwhi_87928\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolatetartwithwhi_87928_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate tart with white chocolate sauce\n', ' A superbly rich chocolate tart served with a sweet white chocolate sauce and raspberries. A brilliant make-ahead dinner party dessert.\n', 120, 90, 10, 12),
(2605, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bacon_and_mushroom_61984\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bacon_and_mushroom_61984_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bacon and mushroom frittata\n', ' Frittata is great for a quick brunch. This dish with bacon, mushroom and chives is filled with protein for the perfect start to your day.\n With a GI of 54 this meal is high protein, low GI.\n', 30, 30, 4, 12),
(2606, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/prawn_banh_mi_mini_94362\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/butternut_squash_and_50241\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/butternut_squash_and_50241_16x9.jpg\n', ' Butternut squash curry with cauliflower \'rice\'\n Vegetable curry is a good choice when you’re on a diet because vegetables are so low in calories, which means you can have a generous portion. This very low-calorie dish provides three of your five-a-day. It\'s also vegan.\n Each serving provides 300 kcal,11g protein, 40g carbohydrate (of which 27g sugars), 8g fat (of which 0.5g saturates), 12.5g fibre and 1.3g salt.\n \n', 30, 30, 1, 12),
(2607, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/troteripieneelegates_86355\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282dg3.jpg\n', 'Stuffed trout and purple sprouting broccoli\n', ' None\n', 30, 30, 4, 17),
(2608, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/suriani_home-style_57083\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/suriani_home-style_57083_16x9.jpg\n', 'Suriani home-style chicken curry (‘ishtu’)\n', ' An aromatic and spicy chicken stew served with coconut-flavoured rice.\n', 90, 90, 4, 24),
(2609, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_and_ale_stew_with_39262\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beef_and_ale_stew_with_39262_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beef and ale stew with dumplings\n', ' Beef and ale stew is the most traditional of slow-cooked British classics, and is a corker of a one-pot winter warmer.\n', 30, 120, 4, 22),
(2610, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ham_and_eggs_with_88506\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/ham_and_eggs_with_88506_16x9.jpg\n', 'Ham and eggs with grilled tomato\n', ' Serve a few slices of sourdough bread with prosciutto, creamy scrambled eggs and grilled tomato for a lazy weekend breakfast or brunch.\n', 30, 30, 1, 9),
(2611, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/aubergine_and_mozzarella_51464\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/aubergine_and_mozzarella_51464_16x9.jpg\n', 'Aubergine and mozzarella bake \n', ' A simple vegetarian bake made with mozzarella and aubergine will out-class any lasagne ready-meal. Serve with crusty bread. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n', 30, 90, 4, 9),
(2612, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lamb_masala_85568\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lamb_masala_85568_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lamb masala\n', ' The lamb in this rich curry is gently poached in spiced water to make sure it is tender and flavoured right through.\n', 30, 120, 4, 20),
(2613, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/scones_35420\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/scones_35420_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cherry scones\n', ' This easy recipe for cherry scones is perfect for a quick afternoon treat or for cooking with the kids.\n', 30, 30, 8, 7),
(2614, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/zoubidas_lamb_tagine_90479\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/porkfilletstroganoff_73432\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/porkfilletstroganoff_73432_16x9.jpg\n', ' Pork stroganoff\n Pork fillet is a really tender cut so great for quick-cook dishes like Mary\'s creamy stroganoff.\n', 30, 30, 4, 12),
(2615, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lighter_lamb_hotpot_14339\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lighter_lamb_hotpot_14339_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lighter lamb hotpot\n', ' A hearty meal for four in one pot. Tender lamb cooked in a richly flavoured casserole with crisp layered potatoes on top.\n Each serving provides 455 kcal, 31g protein, 47g carbohydrate (of which 13g sugars), 14g fat (of which 5g saturates), 10g fibre and 1.7g salt. \n', 30, 120, 4, 16),
(2616, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/panfriedjohndoryingr_85340\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vzb8.jpg\n', 'Pan-fried John Dory with warm apple salad\n', ' None\n', 90, 30, 4, 25),
(2617, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_chocolate_cookies_04207\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_chocolate_cookies_04207_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan chocolate chip cookies\n', ' It only takes about half an hour to get a batch of these vegan chocolate chip cookies baked – then it’s just a matter of waiting for them to cool! \n Each serving provides 203 kcal, 2g protein, 27g carbohydrate (of which 17g sugars), 10g fat (of which 3g saturates), 0.8g fibre and 0.3g salt.\n', 30, 30, 20, 10),
(2618, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastbeefandyorkshir_93184\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_cooker_split_pea_93320\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow_cooker_split_pea_93320_16x9.jpg\n', ' Slow cooker dal\n Tasty and filling, dal makes a cheap, healthy and satisfying meal.Try freezing it in portion-sized containers - it will keep for up to 2 months.\n \n Each serving provides 356kcal, 19g protein, 46g carbohydrate (of which 6g sugars),	9g fat (of which 1g saturates), 8g fibre and	1g salt.\n', 30, 120, 4, 13),
(2619, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_mussel_soup_72720\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vvb6.jpg\n', 'Spiced mussel soup \n', ' A light, creamy seafood soup flavoured with fennel, garlic and a touch of curry powder. \n', 30, 30, 4, 19),
(2620, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastribsoftradition_67339\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/courgetti_spaghetti_with_07741\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/courgetti_spaghetti_with_07741_16x9.jpg\n', ' Courgetti with vegan pesto \n This quick, gluten-free, vegan courgetti is a delicious and healthy alternative to traditional pasta pesto.\n Equipment and preparation: For this recipe, you will need a julienne peeler.\n \n This meal provides 378 kcal, 10g protein, 14g carbohydrate (of which 5g sugars), 31g fat (of which 6g saturates), 11g fibre and 0.9g salt per portion. \n \n', 30, 0, 4, 13),
(2621, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/gnocchi_with_wild_rocket_14134\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/gnocchi_with_wild_rocket_14134_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gnocchi with wild rocket\n', ' Gennaro makes his gnocchi with boiled potatoes - much faster than baking them - and serves them in an easy rocket, basil and chilli sauce. \n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(2622, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_croquetas_with_26131\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/citrustartwithrichsh_90187\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/citrustartwithrichsh_90187_16x9.jpg\n', ' Citrus tart with rich shortcrust pastry\n Equipment and preparation: You\'ll need a 24cm/9in loose-bottomed flan ring.\n', 90, 120, 6, 14);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(2623, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/classic_chocolate_clair_72793\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fried_corned_beef_and_60973\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sunken_chocolate_42872\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sunken_chocolate_42872_16x9.jpg\n Sunken chocolate amaretto cake\n This is one of those dark, squidgy-bellied chocolate cakes that I turn to gratefully when I have friends over to supper; a gratitude that is always reciprocated. The mixture of ground almonds and amaretto gives a marzipan kick, balancing the bitterness of the chocolate. The amaretti cream alongside brings both smoothness and a fine honeycomb crunch to the velvetiness of the cake. \n Equipment: You will need a 20cm/8in springform cake tin.\n', 30, 90, 10, 10),
(2624, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cheddarandhameggybre_72058\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cheddarandhameggybre_72058_16x9.jpg\n', 'French toast with ham and cheddar\n', ' It might not be for everyday, but when you need a proper breakfast this will really hit the spot. As it\'s all cooked in one pan, it\'s a good recipe for camping too.\n', 30, 10, 2, 9),
(2625, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/aromaticporkbellyhot_10468\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282bb4.jpg\n', 'Aromatic pork belly hotpot\n', ' None\n', 30, 120, 6, 12),
(2626, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_vegetarian_tacos_88736\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_vegetarian_tacos_88736_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy vegetarian tacos\n', ' Vegetarian tacos are fun and easy to make. Everyone can help themselves to the crunchy corn tacos, spicy bean filling, creamy avocado, soured cream and grated cheese.\n If you\'re making this recipe with children, see the tips section for advice on kitchen safety.  \n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(2627, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/upside-down_pie_97366\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/upside-down_pie_97366_16x9.jpg\n', 'Upside-down apple pie with butterscotch sauce\n', ' No need to make a separate caramel for this tarte tatin, just let the butter and sugar do its thing in the oven. Serve with a creamy butterscotch sauce and good vanilla ice cream.\n', 30, 120, 6, 11),
(2628, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/saffron_chicken_korma_69369\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/monkfish_bourguignon_29096\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p047mhsl.jpg\n', ' Monkfish Bourguignon\n Meaty monkfish makes a great subsitute for pescatarians in this twist on the classic bourguignon.\n', 30, 90, 1, 12),
(2629, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/marjolaine_71611\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/marjolaine_71611_16x9.jpg\n', 'Marjolaine\n', ' This cake combines layers of nutty meringue, praline buttercream and chocolate ganache. It’s naturally gluten-free, too. \n For this recipe you will need 2 x 30x20cm/12x8in Swiss roll tins, a freestanding electric mixer with a whisk attachment, a piping bag with a small star nozzle (no. 33) and a food processor. \n', 90, 120, 10, 13),
(2630, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roast_daurade_gilthead_11728\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p028qvvh.jpg\n', 'Roast daurade (gilt-head bream) with Parma ham and rosemary butter sauce\n', ' Try daurade as an alternative to cod  - it’s delicious on the barbecue in this simple recipe served with a rich rosemary sauce.\n', 30, 30, 4, 17),
(2631, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pulled_pork_goan-style_86037\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/boiledcollarofbaconw_90922\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vymn.jpg\n', ' Boiled collar of bacon with vegetables and dumplings\n None\n', 480, 120, 4, 19),
(2632, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fruity_yoghurt_jellies_38771\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fruity_yoghurt_jellies_38771_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fruity yoghurt jellies\n', ' These little yoghurt jellies are sweetened with no-added-sugar cordial and will hit the spot if you are used to finishing a meal with dessert. The yoghurt brings extra protein and the jellies are topped with mixed berries for fibre. Leaf gelatine is very simple to use and easily available – so give it a go.\n With a GI of 39 this meal is high protein, low GI and provides 42 kcal per portion.\n \n', 120, 10, 4, 7),
(2633, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/shrimpravioliwithshr_85426\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07f3qv9.jpg\n', 'Shrimp ravioli with shrimp and tomato sauce\n', ' None\n', 120, 10, 4, 13),
(2634, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/curried_carrot_soup_29946\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/curried_carrot_soup_29946_16x9.jpg\n', 'Curried carrot soup\n', ' This lightly spiced carrot soup is so simple to make, yet it makes a delicious supper on a cold winter\'s evening.\n', 30, 30, 4, 9),
(2635, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mulled_wine_trifle_96060\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vx7p.jpg\n', 'Spiced mulled wine trifle \n', ' If you don’t have time to make the nutmeg-flavoured Madeira cake for this Christmas trifle ahead of time, simply buy a plain version to make this spiced festive dessert.\n', 480, 90, 6, 21),
(2636, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/griddle_pan_pumpkin_16498\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/griddle_pan_pumpkin_16498_16x9.jpg\n', 'Griddle pan pumpkin waffles\n', ' Make brunch seasonal by adding pumpkin or squash to your waffles. No waffle iron? No problem! These are made in a griddle pan.\n We used a 26x26cm/10x10in griddle pan, if you use a larger pan the mixture will make fewer waffles. \n', 30, 90, 4, 11),
(2637, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/white_chocolate_wedding_01746\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/white_chocolate_wedding_01746_16x9.jpg\n', 'White chocolate wedding cake\n', ' This white chocolate wedding cake is a chocoholic\'s dream!  For this recipe you’ll need a 23cm/9in round cake tin and board and a 15cm/6in round cake tin and board. You will also need four dowelling rods and four cake pillars (available from specialist cake shops).\n', 90, 120, 60, 10),
(2638, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tandoori_quail_with_91053\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0282c64.jpg\n', 'Tandoori quail with fennel salad and yoghurt dressing\n', ' Fire up the griddle-pan for a tasty tandoori quail recipe.\n', 480, 30, 4, 19),
(2639, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cauliflower_cheese_27559\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07f3sp4.jpg\n', 'Classic cauliflower cheese\n', ' Cauliflower cheese is a perfect side dish for roast chicken – either as part of a Sunday dinner or with cold leftovers.\n', 30, 90, 4, 12),
(2640, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastvegetablesoup_6537\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastvegetablesoup_6537_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roast vegetable soup\n', ' This healthy roasted vegetable soup can be made super quickly if you use a bag of frozen roast veg from a supermarket. \n', 30, 90, 2, 8),
(2641, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/redsnapperwithcoconu_86477\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p027vflf.jpg\n', 'Red snapper with coconut and pineapple salsa\n', ' None\n', 30, 30, 2, 14),
