(3492, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/warm_cherry_soup_15890\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/hearty_winter_mussels_45629\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/galaktoboureko_with_27774\n', ' https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/galaktoboureko_with_27774_16x9.jpg\n Galaktoboureko with orange syrup\n The Greeks love their sweets, and this one is almost as central to their cooking culture as baklava or rice pudding. It is quite common to add an orange sauce to galaktoboureko. I made this one typically sweet and sticky.\n', 30, 90, 8, 10),
(3493, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_bread_sauce_26387\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_bread_sauce_26387_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy bread sauce\n', ' Classic bread sauce is a British classic perfect with any white meat, but especially Christmas turkey!\n It can easily be made ahead of time too, win-win.\n', 30, 30, 6, 8),
