(3501, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/whitesauce_1298\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/whitesauce_1298_16x9.jpg\n', 'White sauce\n', ' This basic white sauce recipe is so versatile, and can be dressed-up or dressed-down for any occasion. \n Each serving provides 657 kcal, 23g protein, 46g carbohydrates (of which 27g sugars), 43g fat (of which 27g saturates), 1g fibre and 2.1g salt.\n', 30, 30, 1, 5),
