(3505, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/herby_skyr_chicken_salad_90551\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/herby_skyr_chicken_salad_90551_16x9.jpg\n', 'Herby chicken and potato salad\n', ' Skyr is an Icelandic yoghurt that is starting to appear in our supermarkets. It is good with chicken because it takes other flavours well and helps the meat get lovely and tender. \n', 30, 30, 2, 15),
