(3661, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mediterranean_roasted_51424\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mediterranean_roasted_51424_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roasted vegetables three ways \n', ' Roast a tray of vegetables when you have the time and keep them in the fridge to turn into delicious nutritious meals in minutes. Eat them as a side or follow our easy recipes for a tasty salad or an oven-baked frittata. \n', 30, 90, 12, 24),
