(3667, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/parmigiana_melanzana_74675\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/popcorn_pork_tiger_82171\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickpea_patty_35509\n', ' https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cherry_bakewell_fondant_20118\n https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cherry_bakewell_fondant_20118_16x9.jpg\n Cherry Bakewell fondant fancies \n Almonds and cherries are a great combination - used to great effect in these pretty individual cakes.\n For this recipe you will need a freestanding mixer with a whisk and beater attachment, a deep 23cm/9in square cake tin and a piping bag fitted with a medium star nozzle.\n', 90, 120, 25, 17),
