(4074, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pineapple_with_star_29786\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/course_country_terrine_54023\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/course_country_terrine_54023_16x9.jpg\n', ' Coarse country terrine\n Don\'t be put off by making a terrine - they\'re really easy once you know how.Equipment and preparation: You’ll need a 1.1 litre/2 pint lidded terrine mould\n', 120, 120, 10, 18),
