(4371, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/miso_ramen_soup_with_15548\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/miso_ramen_soup_with_15548_16x9.jpg\n', 'Miso ramen soup with buckwheat noodles\n', ' This comforting, gluten-free broth is packed with fresh vegetables, while the miso paste brings great depth of flavour. Making your own bone broth adds extra goodness. \n This meal provides 458 kcal, 20g protein, 72.5g carbohydrate (of which 8.5g sugars), 10g fat (of which 0.8g saturates), 9g fibre and 3g salt per portion. \n \n \n', 120, 10, 4, 22),
