(5829, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/yorkshire_puddings_with_15870\n', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mackerel_with_rhubarb_97633\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mackerel_with_rhubarb_97633_16x9.jpg\n', ' Mackerel with rhubarb chutney and orange and chicory salad\n Tangy rhubarb really complements the rich, oily mackerel and a light citrus salad rounds it all off perfectly.\n', 30, 30, 2, 18),
